description:
Discover the perfect blend of style, capability, and technology in the 2023 Hyundai Tucson SEL. This stunning SUV is a true standout, offering a remarkable driving experience that seamlessly combines power, efficiency, and advanced features.

Boasting a striking Black exterior, the Tucson SEL commands attention with its bold presence. Under the hood, a 2.5L I4 DGI DOHC 16V LEV3-ULEV70 engine delivers an impressive 187 horsepower, paired with an 8-Speed Automatic with SHIFTRONIC transmission and all-wheel drive capabilities. With an EPA-estimated 23 MPG in the city and 28 MPG on the highway, this Tucson delivers exceptional fuel economy, making it a practical and eco-friendly choice.

Key features include:
• Convenience Package with Ambient Interior Lighting, Power Sunroof, and more
• Tow Hitch for added versatility
• Front and Rear Mudguards for enhanced protection

The Tucson SEL also boasts a wealth of advanced technologies, including a 10.25" Digital Instrument Cluster, Apple CarPlay & Android Auto integration, and an Auto-Dimming Interior Mirror with Homelink. The Leather-Wrapped Steering Wheel and Shift Knob add a touch of sophistication, while the Heated Front Bucket Seats ensure maximum comfort.

As a Hyundai Certified Used Vehicle, this Tucson SEL comes with an impressive array of benefits, including a 173+ Point Inspection, Roadside Assistance, a Limited Warranty, and a Powertrain Limited Warranty. You can have peace of mind knowing that this vehicle has been meticulously inspected and backed by Hyundai's commitment to quality.

Experience the exceptional value, performance, and features of the 2023 Hyundai Tucson SEL. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate how this remarkable SUV can enhance your driving experience.

description: Discover the Thrill of the Open Road with the 2023 Ford Bronco Sport Big Bend in Cactus Gray Adventure Awaits in Every Mile. For those who crave adventure and the freedom of the open road, the 2023 Ford Bronco Sport Big Bend is your perfect companion. Its robust 1.5L Ecoboost engine, paired with a responsive 8-speed automatic transmission, delivers a turbocharged performance that s both powerful and efficient. The striking Cactus Gray exterior not only turns heads but also embodies the rugged spirit of this versatile 4D Sport Utility vehicle. Safety is paramount, with features like Blind Spot Monitor, Lane Keeping Assist, and Front Collision Mitigation ensuring peace of mind on every journey. The Bronco Sport s advanced Driver Monitoring and Cross-Traffic Alert systems further enhance your driving confidence, whether navigating city streets or exploring off-the-beaten-path trails. Inside, the Bronco Sport offers a seamless blend of comfort and technology. Enjoy the convenience of Keyless Start and Smart Device Integration, while the Back-Up Camera and Bluetooth Connection keep you connected and aware. The spacious interior, featuring bucket seats and a pass-through rear seat, provides ample room for both passengers and gear, making it ideal for weekend getaways or spontaneous road trips. Embrace the adventure with the Ford Bronco Sport Big Bend. Be sure to call or visit Vandergriff Toyota to discover more. Your new favorite vehicle awaits - don't let someone else drive it home!

The Enclave's 3.6L V6 engine and 9-speed automatic transmission deliver a smooth and responsive ride, while the front-wheel-drive configuration provides confident handling. With an EPA-estimated 18 MPG in the city and 26 MPG on the highway, this Enclave offers impressive fuel efficiency for its size and capability.

Step inside and you'll be greeted by a spacious and well-appointed interior. The Buick Infotainment System with SiriusXM Satellite Radio keeps you entertained, while the dual-zone automatic climate control ensures everyone rides in comfort. The power driver's seat and heated front seats add an extra touch of luxury, and the 7-passenger seating provides ample room for the whole family.

Safety is also a top priority, with features like OnStar Guidance, Rear Parking Sensors, and a suite of airbags to give you peace of mind on the road. The Enclave's sleek exterior design is complemented by 18-inch painted aluminum wheels, a roof rack, and a power liftgate for added convenience.

Whether you're embarking on a family road trip or navigating your daily commute, this 2018 Buick Enclave Essence is the perfect companion. Experience the perfect blend of style, comfort, and capability – all at an exceptional value.

Discover the versatility and capability of the 2021 Ford Transit-250 Base 148" EL Hi Rf 9070 GVWR RWD. This powerful and adaptable van is the perfect choice for your business or personal transportation needs.

Equipped with a V6 engine and 10-Speed Automatic transmission with Overdrive, this Transit-250 delivers impressive performance and efficiency. Key features include:

• Back-up Cam
• Bluetooth
• Cruise Control
• Extended
• High Roof
• Lane Keeping Assist

• Load Area Protection Package

The Load Area Protection Package provides durable, easy-to-clean surfaces throughout the cargo area, ensuring your valuables stay secure and protected. The Cruise Control with Adjustable Speed Limiting Device allows you to maintain a safe, consistent speed, even in city traffic. The fixed rear cargo door glass enhances visibility and convenience when loading and unloading.

With its spacious 148" extended length and high roof, this Transit-250 offers ample room for transporting equipment, materials, or even passengers. The rear-wheel-drive configuration provides excellent traction and control, making it a reliable workhorse for any job.

Beyond the practical features, this Transit-250 also boasts a range of comfort and convenience amenities. Enjoy the convenience of Bluetooth connectivity, power windows, and steering wheel-mounted audio controls. The rear-window defroster and air conditioning will keep you comfortable in any weather.

Backed by Ford's reputation for quality and durability, the 2021 Transit-250 is a smart investment for your business or personal transportation needs. Experience the versatility and capability that this van has to offer. Visit our showroom today to take a test drive and discover why the Transit-250 is the perfect fit for you.

The 10-speed automatic transmission with Traction Select System ensures that you have the right power at your fingertips, adapting to any terrain with ease. With quad bucket seats and a spacious third row, the Yukon Denali is designed for families and adventurers alike, providing comfort and versatility for every journey. This Yukon Denali is not just a vehicle, its a statement of sophistication and capability, ready to elevate your driving experience. Are you ready to embrace the journey?   • Cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful, until cruise control set the pace. Safety and Security

  • Selective Internet access - a more focused delivery. Selective internet access allows you to tailor the features for your feed, such as sports scores, local news, or current weather. When it comes to getting what you want, selective internet access is a net gain.

''The 2023 Chrysler Pacifica is an ideal people-hauler with spacious seating in all three rows, plenty of cargo space and lots of standard features,'' U.S. News writes. Key 2023 Chrysler Pacifica Awards & Recognition: IIHS TOP SAFETY PICK: Earned for the 2023 model year, marking7 consecutive years of top safety recognition for the minivan. Car and Driver Editors' Choice (2023): Recognized for the 7th consecutive year. Top Safety Ratings: Achieved 'Good' ratings in driver-side, passenger-side, and moderate overlap frontal impacts. A 3.6-liter V6 (287 horsepower, 262 lb-ft) engine is standard on the Pacifica, and it powers the minivan's front wheels through a nine-speed automatic transmission. The 2023 Chrysler Pacifica is an ideal people-hauler with spacious seating in all three rows, plenty of cargo space and lots of standard features. With its odometer now hovering around the 21,499 mark, it is STILL COVERED under the balance of the factory BUMPER-TO-BUMPER warranty until October 2026 or 36,000 miles (whichever occurs first)! Additionally, its engine, transmission and drive axles will be covered by the remainder of the POWERTRAIN warranty until 2029 or 60,000 miles! description:
Discover the exceptional 2024 Lexus RX 350 Premium, a vehicle that combines sophisticated style, advanced technology, and uncompromising performance. This captivating SUV is the perfect blend of luxury and capability, designed to elevate your driving experience.

• Cold Area Package
• Radio: Lexus Interface w/14" HD Touchscreen Display
• Power Rear Door w/Kick Sensor
• 19" Wheels
• Navigation System
• 12 Speakers
• Air Conditioning
• Power Driver Seat
• Steering Wheel Mounted Audio Controls
• 4-Wheel Disc Brakes
• Power Moonroof
• Power Liftgate
• Exterior Parking Camera Rear
• Heated & Ventilated Front Bucket Seats
• Wireless Apple CarPlay/Wireless Android Auto

Powered by a 2.4L I4 PDI Turbocharged engine, the 2024 Lexus RX 350 Premium delivers a thrilling 275 horsepower, effortlessly propelling you down the road with confidence. Paired with an 8-speed automatic transmission and all-wheel drive, this SUV offers a smooth, responsive, and capable driving experience, no matter the conditions.

Elevate your commute or weekend adventures with the RX 350 Premium's exceptional fuel efficiency, achieving an impressive 21 MPG in the city and 28 MPG on the highway. This remarkable balance of power and efficiency makes the RX 350 Premium an ideal choice for those seeking a premium driving experience without sacrificing practicality.

Step inside the RX 350 Premium and discover a cabin that exudes refinement and attention to detail. Luxurious NuLuxe seating, a heated steering wheel, and a panoramic moonroof create an inviting and comfortable environment, while the Lexus Interface with a 14-inch touchscreen display provides intuitive control over the vehicle's advanced technology features.

Safety is paramount in the 2024 Lexus RX 350 Premium, with a comprehensive suite of driver-assistance technologies, including Blind Spot Monitoring, Rear Cross-Traffic Alert, and a Surround View Camera System. These cutting-edge features work in harmony to help keep you and your loved ones secure on the road.

Experience the pinnacle of luxury SUV design and engineering with the 2024 Lexus RX 350 Premium. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate how this exceptional vehicle can elevate your driving experience. 2021 Jeep Wrangler Unlimited Rubicon Low Miles • Legendary 4WD • Trail-Rated Capability

VIN: 1C4HJXFG8MW560865
Stock #: 22371
Mileage: 19,273
Exterior: Black Clearcoat
Interior: Black
Drivetrain: 4WD
Engine: 3.6L V6 24V VVT
Transmission: 8-Speed Automatic

The 2021 Jeep Wrangler Unlimited Rubicon is the benchmark for off-road capability, blending legendary Jeep toughness with modern comfort and technology. Finished in classic Black Clearcoat over a durable black interior, this Rubicon offers a rugged, purpose-built appearance that never goes out of style. With only 19,273 miles, this example presents an outstanding opportunity to own a low-mileage, highly capable Wrangler that is equally at home on the trail or the street.

Power comes from Jeeps proven 3.6L V6 engine, delivering dependable performance and smooth power delivery across a wide range of driving conditions. Paired with the responsive 8-speed automatic transmission, this Wrangler offers confident acceleration, excellent low-speed control off-road, and relaxed highway cruising. The Rubicon trim is engineered for serious adventure, featuring heavy-duty components designed to conquer challenging terrain with ease.

Equipped with Jeeps Trail Rated capability, the Rubicon includes advanced 4WD hardware, rock-crawling gearing, and rugged suspension tuning that set it apart from standard Wranglers. Whether navigating rocky trails, muddy paths, snow-covered roads, or sandy beaches, this Wrangler is built to perform where others stop. At the same time, the four-door Unlimited configuration provides added practicality, offering easy rear-seat access and extra cargo space for gear, passengers, or daily errands.

Inside, the cabin balances durability with comfort. The black interior is designed to withstand the elements while still providing modern amenities and intuitive controls. Upright seating, excellent visibility, and a commanding driving position contribute to the Wranglers unmistakable driving experience. Removable doors and roof panels allow you to enjoy open-air driving, a signature feature that continues to define the Wrangler lifestyle.

The 2021 Wrangler Unlimited Rubicon is ideal for buyers who want a vehicle that can handle daily driving during the week and serious off-road adventures on the weekend. Its strong resale value, proven reliability, and unmatched off-road pedigree make it one of the most desirable SUVs in its class.

Key Features & Highlights:

3.6L V6 24V VVT Engine

8-Speed Automatic Transmission

Advanced 4WD System

Rubicon Trail-Rated Off-Road Capability

Four-Door Unlimited Configuration

Removable Roof and Doors

Low Mileage Example

Two Lynnwood, WA locations

4.6 Google and 4.8 Carfax ratings

Hand-selected inventory and transparent process

Competitive financing options available

description:
The 2025 BMW X2 xDrive28i is a remarkable compact crossover that seamlessly blends style, performance, and advanced technology. This stunning vehicle boasts a sleek, modern exterior design that commands attention, while its spacious and well-appointed interior offers a premium driving experience.

Highlighted features include:
• Navigation System
• 7 Speakers
• SiriusXM with 360L and 1 Year Platinum Plan Subscription
• Dual-Zone Automatic Climate Control
• Power Driver's Seat with Memory Function
• Four-Wheel Independent Suspension
• ABS Brakes and Electronic Stability Control

The BMW X2 xDrive28i is powered by a 2.0L 4-Cylinder DOHC 16V TwinPower Turbo engine, delivering an impressive balance of power and efficiency with 24 city and 33 highway MPG. The 7-speed automatic transmission and all-wheel-drive system ensure a dynamic and responsive driving experience, whether navigating city streets or exploring open roads.

This BMW X2 is not only well-equipped but also meticulously maintained. With just 8,671 miles on the odometer, it has been thoroughly inspected and certified to meet the highest standards of quality and reliability. You can drive with confidence, knowing that this vehicle has been rigorously tested and is backed by BMW's renowned reputation for exceptional engineering and craftsmanship.

The interior of the X2 is a sanctuary of refined luxury, featuring perforated Veganza upholstery, heated front seats, and a widescreen display that seamlessly integrates your smartphone's Apple CarPlay and Android Auto capabilities. The spacious cargo area and split-folding rear seats provide ample versatility, making this BMW an ideal choice for both everyday commuting and weekend adventures.

Safety is paramount in the X2, with a comprehensive suite of advanced driver-assistance technologies, including a Rear View Camera, Automatic High-Beam Headlights, and BMW Assist eCall for added peace of mind.

This 2025 BMW X2 xDrive28i is a remarkable opportunity to own a meticulously maintained, feature-rich, and stylish compact crossover. Experience the exceptional craftsmanship, performance, and technology that define the BMW brand. Schedule a test drive today and discover the true joy of driving.

description:
Discover the ultimate in power, capability, and comfort with this remarkable 2019 GMC Sierra 1500 SLT. This truck is meticulously engineered to deliver an unparalleled driving experience, whether you're tackling tough terrain or cruising down the highway.

Packed with an impressive array of features, this Sierra SLT stands out from the crowd. Highlights include:

• SLT PREMIUM PLUS PACKAGE
• X31 OFF-ROAD PACKAGE
• REAR UNDERSEAT STORAGE, COMPOSITE STORAGE BIN
• TIRES, 275/60R20SL ALL-TERRAIN, BLACKWALL

The Sierra's EcoTec3 5.3L V8 engine, paired with an 8-speed automatic transmission and 4-wheel drive, provides the perfect blend of power and efficiency, delivering 15 city/21 highway mpg. With its rugged off-road capabilities and advanced driver assistance technologies, this truck is ready to handle any adventure you have in mind.

Inside, you'll be surrounded by premium amenities that elevate your driving experience. Enjoy the comfort of heated and ventilated front seats, a heated steering wheel, and a premium Bose audio system. Stay connected with the advanced GMC Infotainment System, complete with navigation, Apple CarPlay, and Android Auto.

Safety is a top priority, and this Sierra SLT is equipped with a comprehensive suite of advanced driver assistance features, including Forward Collision Alert, Lane Keep Assist, and Rear Cross Traffic Alert. You can drive with confidence, knowing you and your passengers are well-protected.

With its striking White Frost Tricoat exterior and spacious Crew Cab design, this 2019 GMC Sierra 1500 SLT is a true head-turner. Its impressive capabilities, refined interior, and cutting-edge technology make it the ultimate choice for those seeking a versatile and sophisticated full-size pickup.

We invite you to experience the power and luxury of this remarkable Sierra SLT for yourself. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate how this exceptional truck can transform your driving experience.

description: Welcome to Dave Mungenast St. Louis Honda. We are one of the St. Louis area's largest Honda dealers. Founded in 1965 the Mungenast family has served the St. Louis area with its automotive needs for 60 years. As the #1 volume Honda dealership in Missouri for 33 consecutive years, a 18-time president's award winner, a Honda Master Circle Award Winner, and a 4-time BBB Torch award winner, we are proud to serve the community with honest and transparent business practices. Experience luxury and versatility with this dark gray 2023 Honda Odyssey Elite! Designed for families and road trips, this top-trim minivan offers premium leather-trimmed upholstery, heated and ventilated front seats, and a spacious interior with seating for up to eight. Stay entertained with a 10.2-inch rear video monitor, Blu-Ray/DVD player, and wireless headphones, while rear seat passengers enjoy dedicated USB outlets. The Honda Sensing suite adds peace of mind with adaptive cruise control, lane keeping assist, front automatic emergency braking, and pedestrian detection. Enjoy modern conveniences such as a hands-free power liftgate, one-touch power sliding doors, rain-sensing wipers, and a panoramic moonroof. Stay connected with Apple CarPlay, Android Auto, built-in navigation, wireless charging, Wi-Fi hotspot, and HondaLink app integration. The powerful 3.5L V6 engine, 10-speed automatic transmission, and smooth FWD make every drive enjoyable. • Remote keyless entry

The Camry's 2.5L I4 DOHC 16V engine delivers a smooth and responsive driving experience, with an impressive 28 city/39 highway MPG rating. You'll enjoy the confidence and control that comes with the 8-speed automatic transmission and front-wheel drive.

Inside, the Camry SE offers a well-appointed cabin with premium features that elevate your daily commute. Enjoy the convenience of the power driver's seat, steering wheel-mounted audio controls, and the intuitive infotainment system with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto integration. Stay connected and entertained on the go.

Safety is a top priority in this Camry, with a comprehensive suite of advanced driver-assistance technologies. Features like the Rear Camera, Automatic High Beams, and the Safety Connect emergency communication system provide added peace of mind, whether you're navigating city streets or highway driving.

The exterior of this Camry SE exudes a sporty and modern aesthetic, with the sleek White paint and 18-inch Black Machined-Finish Alloy wheels. The bold front grille and sculpted body lines give this sedan a dynamic and eye-catching presence on the road.

This 2021 Toyota Camry SE is a remarkable value, priced at just $21,000. With its impressive features, exceptional fuel efficiency, and Toyota's renowned reliability, this Camry is an exceptional choice for the discerning buyer.

Mosaic Auto Group: One Name. One Location. One Goal. "Bring trust in car buying and passion into service."

This 2022 Chevrolet Silverado 1500 LTD High Country Trailering Package is a true workhorse, packed with premium features that will elevate your driving experience. Let's explore why this truck should be at the top of your list.

• Service Records Available
• CLEAN CAR FAX
• Preferred Equipment Group 3LZ
• Trailering Package
• Up-Level Rear Seat w/Storage Package
• Navigation System
• Rear Dual USB Charging-Only Ports
• Steering Wheel Audio Controls
• Wireless Phone Projection
• Electric Rear-Window Defogger
• 120-Volt Bed Mounted Power Outlet
• 120-Volt Instrument Panel Power Outlet
• Bluetooth® For Phone
• Driver Memory
• Power Front Passenger Windows w/Express Up/Down
• Remote Vehicle Starter System

This Silverado's powerful 6.2L V8 EcoTec3 engine and 10-speed automatic transmission deliver exceptional performance and capability, with 4WD for confident all-weather driving. The High Country Trailering Package further enhances its towing and hauling prowess, making it the perfect companion for your next adventure.

Inside, the spacious and well-appointed cabin features premium leather seating, heated and ventilated front seats, and a Bose premium audio system. The advanced technology suite includes a large 8-inch driver information center, wireless charging, and a state-of-the-art infotainment system with navigation, Apple CarPlay, and Android Auto.

Safety and driver assistance features are also a priority, with lane change alert, rear cross-traffic alert, and front and rear park assist to help you navigate with confidence. The Silverado's robust construction and comprehensive suite of airbags provide added peace of mind.

This 2022 Chevrolet Silverado 1500 LTD High Country Trailering Package is a true standout in the full-size truck segment, blending premium comfort, advanced technology, and uncompromising capability. Experience the difference for yourself – schedule a test drive today.

description:
Elevate your driving experience with this exceptional 2019 GMC Sierra 1500 SLT. Boasting a powerful EcoTec3 5.3L V8 engine paired with an 8-Speed Automatic transmission and 4-Wheel Drive, this truck is primed for both work and play.

Highlighted features include:
• SLT Premium Package
• Driver Alert Package I
• Max Trailering Package
• Perimeter Lighting
• Heated and Ventilated Front Seats
• Heated Rear Outboard Seats
• 20" Polished Aluminum Wheels
• Integrated Trailer Brake Controller
• In-Vehicle Trailering App
• Power Sliding Rear Window
• Rear Cross Traffic Alert
• Lane Change Alert with Side Blind Zone Alert

This Sierra SLT delivers an unparalleled blend of capability, comfort, and convenience. The premium SLT trim level elevates the driving experience with a host of advanced technologies and luxurious amenities. The powerful EcoTec3 V8 engine provides ample power for towing and hauling, while the 4-Wheel Drive system ensures confident handling in any conditions.

The SLT Premium Package adds a touch of elegance with 20-inch polished aluminum wheels, chrome assist steps, and a chrome grille. The Driver Alert Package I enhances safety with features like Front and Rear Park Assist, Lane Change Alert, and Rear Cross Traffic Alert. The Max Trailering Package equips this Sierra with a heavy-duty rear axle, enhanced cooling, and a 220-amp alternator, making it the ideal companion for your towing needs.

Inside, you'll be surrounded by premium amenities, including heated and ventilated front seats, a heated steering wheel, and a Bose premium audio system. The GMC Infotainment System with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto integration keeps you connected and entertained on the go.

Whether you're tackling tough jobs or seeking a capable and refined daily driver, this 2019 GMC Sierra 1500 SLT is the perfect choice. Visit our showroom today to experience the power, versatility, and premium features of this exceptional truck.

description:
Discover unmatched choice at Westgate Chrysler Jeep Dodge Ram in Raleigh, home to a huge lineup of new vehicles and one of the largest used-car inventories on the east coast with 1,000+ options ready to drive.

This 2016 Lexus NX 200t offers an impressive array of premium features, including:

• Radio: AM/FM/CD Lexus Display Audio
• Automatic temperature control
• Power driver seat
• Steering wheel mounted audio controls
• Exterior Parking Camera Rear
• Fully automatic headlights
• Heated door mirrors
• Power door mirrors
• Alloy wheels

With its sleek gray exterior, this NX 200t combines sophisticated style and advanced technology. The 2.0L 16V DOHC engine provides a spirited yet efficient driving experience, delivering an impressive 22 city/28 highway MPG. Lexus is renowned for its exceptional build quality, and this well-maintained example with just 68,053 miles is a testament to the brand's legendary reliability.

Step inside, and you'll be greeted by a cabin that exudes refinement. Leather-wrapped steering wheel and shift knob, a power-adjustable driver's seat, and dual-zone automatic climate control ensure a comfortable and customized driving experience. The Lexus Display Audio system with SiriusXM radio and a rearview camera make every trip more convenient and connected.

Handling is nimble and responsive, thanks to the four-wheel independent suspension and speed-sensing steering. Safety features like ABS brakes, electronic stability control, and a suite of airbags provide peace of mind on the road.

Whether commuting, running errands, or embarking on a weekend getaway, this 2016 Lexus NX 200t is a versatile and rewarding companion. Its combination of style, performance, and premium amenities make it a standout in the compact luxury SUV segment.

We invite you to experience this exceptional vehicle firsthand. Schedule a test drive today and discover why the Lexus NX 200t should be at the top of your shopping list.

Choose Westgate Chrysler Jeep Dodge Ram in Raleigh, NC for a dealership experience built on transparency, value, and customer-first service. With a wide selection of new CJDR models and an extensive inventory of quality used cars, trucks, and SUVs, Westgate is a trusted destination for shoppers across Raleigh, Durham, the Triangle and all of North Carolina.

Elevate your driving experience with this exceptional 2021 Jeep Grand Cherokee 80th Anniversary Edition. Boasting a sleek Gray exterior and a well-appointed interior, this SUV is the perfect blend of style, capability, and convenience.

Backed by our Lifetime Powertrain Protection, this Grand Cherokee is built to last. Key features include:

• Parallel & Perp Park Assist with Stop
• Adaptive Cruise Control with Stop
• Advanced Brake Assist
• Heavy-Duty Engine Cooling
• Granite Crystal Exterior Accents
• Jeep 80th Anniversary Badges
• Leather Trimmed Bucket Seats

The powerful 3.6L V6 engine, paired with an 8-Speed Automatic transmission and 4WD, delivers an impressive 18 city/25 highway MPG, ensuring a smooth and efficient driving experience. With 55,801 miles, this Grand Cherokee is well-equipped to handle your adventures with ease.

Elevate your commute and weekends with the premium features of this Jeep. The Uconnect 4C Navigation system with an 8.4" touchscreen display keeps you connected and entertained. Dual-zone automatic climate control, a power liftgate, and a panoramic sunroof add to the luxurious cabin experience.

Towing capability is enhanced with the Trailer Tow Group IV, featuring a Class IV receiver hitch, 7- and 4-pin wiring harness, and a full-size spare tire. Whether hauling your boat or camper, this Grand Cherokee is ready for the task.

Safety is a top priority, with features like Full-Speed Forward Collision Warning Plus, Lane Departure Warning Plus, and a ParkView Rear Back-Up Camera providing added peace of mind on the road.

Whether you're seeking a capable family hauler, a versatile adventure companion, or a premium driving experience, this 2021 Jeep Grand Cherokee 80th Anniversary Edition is a must-see. Visit our showroom today to take it for a test drive and discover why it's the perfect addition to your lifestyle.

This 2021 Hyundai Palisade SEL is a premium, feature-rich SUV that's ready to elevate your driving experience. With its striking gray exterior, powerful V6 engine, and advanced all-wheel-drive system, this Palisade is built to handle any road with confidence and style.

Highlighted features include:

• Premium Package with LED taillights, front parking sensors, and a hands-free smart liftgate
• Convenience Package P2 with a 7-inch high-resolution cluster display and wireless phone charging
• Premium Package P3 with heated second-row seats, power-folding third-row seating, and a premium audio system
• Cargo Package with a cargo tray, net, and first aid kit
• Carpeted floor mats and all-season fitted liners for added protection

Step inside and you'll be surrounded by premium touches, including a leather-wrapped steering wheel, genuine leather dashboard, and soft-touch door armrests. The 10.25-inch touchscreen display puts navigation, Apple CarPlay, and Android Auto at your fingertips, while the Harman Kardon premium audio system delivers an immersive listening experience.

Safety and convenience are also top priorities, with features like Highway Driving Assist, Ultrasonic Rear Occupant Alert, and a hands-free smart liftgate. The power-folding third-row seats and generous cargo space make this Palisade perfect for your growing family or active lifestyle.

We utilize Market Based Pricing for all pre-owned vehicles on our lot. This ensures you have the most competitive price in the market based on mileage, equipment, and features. Utilizing this approach, our prices may fluctuate during the day on our website and may not match what is currently on 3rd party sites as they only update every 24 hours. The Suntrup family have been servicing and selling cars since 1957 for the St Louis area. The Suntrup Automotive Group is active in its communities and believes in giving back. Today Suntrup Automotive Group has nine brands, eleven locations, thousands of cars and is every bit committed to providing excellent customer service in every aspect of the business. There's never been a better time to drop on by at our dealership here in 5926 So Lindbergh Blvd St Louis, Missouri, proudly serving drivers from Ballwin, Affton and Kirkwood. Climb inside and discover the thoughtful design and impressive technology that sets the Traverse LS apart. The Chevrolet Infotainment System with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto integration keeps you connected and entertained on the go.

Safety is a top priority, and the Traverse LS delivers with a suite of advanced safety features, including airbags, anti-lock brakes, and electronic stability control. The OnStar and Chevrolet connected services provide added peace of mind, ensuring you can access emergency assistance when needed.

With its spacious 8-passenger seating configuration and split-folding third-row seats, the Traverse LS offers the versatility to accommodate your growing family or active lifestyle. The alloy wheels and rear window wiper add a touch of style and convenience to this well-equipped SUV.

This 2021 Chevrolet Traverse LS is an exceptional value that combines functionality, technology, and safety in a stylish package. Experience the difference for yourself and schedule a test drive today. We're confident you'll be impressed by this exceptional pre-owned SUV.

description: Absolutely stunning and bespoke Bentley Flying Spur Speed First Edition. Powered by a 4.0-liter twin-turbocharged V8 engine with a high-output electric motor and a 25.9 kWh battery pack. The hybrid system allows for silent, all-electric driving when desired, while the V8 delivers unmistakable Bentley performance at speed. 771 horsepower and 738 lb-ft of torque, 0-60 in 3.3 seconds. Finished in Viridian from the Mulliner paint range, the exterior is complemented by 22” 10-swept-spoke wheels in grey with bright machined accents, illuminated by bright polished Flying “B” mascots and enhanced by self-leveling Mulliner wheel badges—subtle details that signal its bespoke nature. Inside, the cabin is trimmed in rich Saddle leather, elevated by the Leather Specification with contrast stitching and seat piping, and anchored by a heated, three-spoke, indented hide steering wheel. The result is a space that feels both modern and unmistakably handcrafted. As a First Edition, this Flying Spur is fully equipped, incorporating Bentley’s Touring, City, and Comfort Specifications, advanced driver-assistance technologies, a head-up display, night vision, surround-view cameras, and front and rear comfort seating with heating, ventilation, and massage. Ambient mood lighting and the Naim for Bentley premium audio system complete an interior designed for effortless long-distance travel or serene electric cruising. MSRP of $348,965.

description: 2015 Rolls-Royce Ghost — English White exterior, Moccasin leather interior. This example is equipped with the factory 6.6L Twin-Turbocharged V12 that produces 563 horsepower and 575 lb-ft of torque, paired with an eight-speed automatic transmission and rear-wheel drive. The powertrain is engineered to deliver effortless acceleration and long-distance cruising capability while remaining refined and composed at all speeds. Fuel economy is factory-rated at approximately 13 MPG city and 21 MPG highway, and this particular vehicle has well under 25,000 miles on the odometer — averaging less than 3,000 miles per year — reflecting light, predominantly highway use and careful ownership. Exterior and presence Finished in English White, the Ghost presents the restrained, formal elegance typical of the model line. The familiar Pantheon grille and Spirit of Ecstasy hood ornament are present in polished metal finish and remain focal points of the design. The sheetmetal is smooth and uncluttered with precise panel gaps and high-quality paint fitment. Standard exterior elements include adaptive xenon/HID headlamps with integrated LED daytime running lights, automatic headlamp operation, and rain-sensing wipers. Power-folding and heated exterior mirrors with integrated turn indicators are factory equipped, along with front and rear park sensors to aid low-speed maneuvering. The vehicle rides on factory alloy wheels with premium all-season tires sized to the original specification, and overall the exterior shows excellent condition consistent with the low mileage. Chassis, suspension and driving dynamics The Ghost’s chassis architecture is designed to isolate occupants from road irregularities while maintaining composure through corners. Factory equipment includes an adaptive air suspension system with automatic leveling and electronically controlled dampers, which adjust to driving conditions to balance ride comfort and body control. Electronic traction and stability control are standard, accompanied by ABS, a full complement of airbags (front, side and curtain), and advanced braking systems with ventilated discs. The transmission features adaptive shift logic to complement the twin-turbo V12’s broad torque curve, providing smooth, decisive downshifts and relaxed highway cruising. Interior appointments and comfort The cabin is trimmed in Moccasin full-grain leather applied throughout the seating surfaces, door panels and center console, with precise hand-stitched seams and attention to fit and finish. Wood veneer trim is integrated into the dash and door tops, selected and finished for grain consistency and tactile smoothness. Front seats are power-adjustable with multiple position memory for the driver, lumbar support and heating elements, they are shaped to provide support for long journeys while presenting a formal seating posture. Rear seating provides plentiful legroom and headroom, with a wide bench and a comfortable cushion — the Ghost’s rear accommodation is focused on passenger comfort and composure. Standard climate control is fully automatic and designed to maintain distinct comfort settings, rear climate controls are provided for passenger convenience. Additional factory comfort features include soft-close doors that close gently under power, power trunk operation, and a multifunction leather-wrapped steering wheel with controls for cruise control, audio and telephone functions. Technology and convenience Factory-fitted infotainment and convenience features include a central display and rotary controller for vehicle and audio systems, navigation system integrated with the vehicle’s electronics to assist in route planning and transmission shift strategy, Bluetooth hands-free phone and audio streaming capability, and a premium audio system with AM/FM, satellite radio capability and multiple input options (USB/AUX). description:
Why BUY from Naples Motorsports Inc.? When you choose this Silver 2016 Rolls-Royce Ghost 4dr Sdn with 12,476 miles, you are not just buying a used vehicle - you are investing in quality, reliability and peace of mind. Our clientele depend on us for Transparent Pricing, Convenience and, most importantly, Customer FIRST Service! No Accidents! What this vehicle includes: Comfort
  • Ventilated front seats -That's cool. Ventilated front seats provides targeted cool air so you and your passenger can get comfortable quicker in hot weather. Getting comfortable is no sweat when you have ventilated front seats.
Convenience
  • Cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful, until cruise control set the pace. Simply set the desired speed using the steering wheel mounted controls and it will maintain that speed without driver intervention. This can help minimize driver fatigue and improve overall fuel economy. Resting your right foot is right at your fingertips thanks to cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls.
  • Power close trunk/liftgate - Dump the slam. You're done loading up, now don't subject your passengers to the ear splitting sound of you slamming the back shut. All you have to do is hit the button and the power close trunk/liftgate takes care of the rest. You can walk away as the Power close trunk/liftgate gently closes and latches.
Safety and Security
  • Brake assist - Stop right there. Something jumps out into the middle of the road and you need to stop now! With brake assist, you will. It uses the speed of the brake pedal's travel to sense panic braking, then applies all available power to boost your stopping power. Brake assist can stop the accident before it is one.
Technology and Telematics
  • Mobile hotspot - WiFi on the fly. Connect your devices to the Internet through your vehicle's private mobile hotspot and take the internet wherever your journey takes you, without eating up your data allowance. Find the hotspot with mobile hotspot.
Come on in to Naples Motorsports Inc. today at 1250 Airport-Pulling Rd S Naples FL 34104 or call (239) 430-5655 to schedule a test drive!

description:
Discover the epitome of luxury and performance in this exquisite 2016 Bentley Mulsanne Base. With its striking white exterior, this Mulsanne exudes a timeless elegance that demands attention wherever it goes.

Meticulously equipped with an impressive array of premium features, this Mulsanne is designed to elevate your driving experience. Highlights include:

• Backup Camera
• Bluetooth
• Heated Seats
• LED Headlights
• Leather Seats
• Memory Seat
• Navigation System
• Premium Sound System
• Sunroof/Moonroof

Beneath the hood, the Mulsanne's powerful 6.8L V8 engine, paired with a smooth-shifting ZF 8-Speed Automatic transmission and rear-wheel drive, delivers an unparalleled blend of power and refinement. With an EPA-estimated 18 mpg on the highway, this Bentley offers a remarkable balance of performance and efficiency.

The Mulsanne's interior is a true sanctuary of comfort and craftsmanship. Luxurious Tamo Ash Veneer and genuine wood accents adorn the dashboard and door panels, creating an atmosphere of timeless elegance. The 14-speaker premium sound system, with features like AM/FM radio, satellite radio, CD player, and a 60-gigabyte hard drive, ensures an immersive listening experience.

Designed to pamper its occupants, the Mulsanne boasts a wealth of comfort-enhancing features, including dual-zone automatic climate control, power-adjustable and heated front seats with memory function, and a power moonroof that floods the cabin with natural light.

Safety is also a top priority, with the Mulsanne equipped with advanced features like adaptive suspension, four-wheel disc brakes with ABS, and a comprehensive airbag system to protect you and your passengers.

This exceptional 2016 Bentley Mulsanne Base, with its low mileage of just 988, represents a rare opportunity to own a true icon of luxury and performance. Experience the unparalleled craftsmanship and refined driving dynamics that have made the Mulsanne a benchmark in the ultra-luxury segment. Schedule a test drive today and discover the difference that a Bentley can make in your driving experience.

Finished in Alpine White and accented by the M Carbon Exterior Package, it carries an aggressive, high-dollar stance that looks as serious as it drives. Offered with nationwide competitive pricing and a recent price adjustment, this BMW delivers unmistakable presence, advanced innovation, and true M-level prestige in one commanding package.

Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
Technology and Telematics
  • Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road.
  • Apple CarPlay smart device wireless mirroring
  • Mobile hotspot - WiFi on the fly. Connect your devices to the Internet through your vehicle's private mobile hotspot and take the internet wherever your journey takes you, without eating up your data allowance. Find the hotspot with mobile hotspot.

description: Originally supposed to be 300 built, with only 35 for the US market. Jaguar actually only built 220 with only 19 coming to the US. This is just one of a couple white specs. Includes the very rare factory car cover Full front PPF with additional PPF on roof, carbon components and behind the wheels Still has factory warranty until the middle of March 2026 may be the only one with original factory warranty left Known as the worlds fastest four door car after it set the Nurburgring lap record for sedans in 2019. One owner purchased in 2021 Jaguar dealer serviced since new Recently replaced all 4 tires Original floor mats still in plastic in the trunk Both remote keys and all literature are included. The 2019 Jaguar Project 8 stands as one of the most extreme and performance-focused vehicles ever produced by the British manufacturer. Developed by Jaguars Special Vehicle Operations (SVO) division, the Project 8 is based on the XE sedan but transformed into a track-capable super saloon. It is powered by a 5.0-liter supercharged V8 engine producing an astonishing 592 horsepower, making it the most powerful road-legal Jaguar at the time of its release. With a lightweight aluminum body, carbon-fiber aerodynamic components, and a race-inspired suspension setup, the Project 8 was engineered to deliver exceptional speed, precision, and driver engagement. What truly sets the 2019 Jaguar Project 8 apart is its exclusivity and motorsport pedigree. each car features aggressive styling cues such as a large front splitter, widened wheel arches, and a prominent rear wing that enhance both performance and visual impact. The cars advanced all-wheel-drive system, eight-speed automatic transmission, and torque vectoring allow it to accelerate from 0 to 60 mph in just 3.3 seconds while maintaining remarkable control on the track. Combining luxury, cutting-edge engineering, and raw performance, the Project 8 represents a bold statement of Jaguars capability to compete with the worlds most elite performance sedans.

description: Step into the realm of unparalleled luxury and sophistication with the 2022 Rolls-Royce Ghost, a masterpiece of automotive engineering that exudes timeless elegance and modern sophistication. With only 4,424 miles on the odometer, this pristine vehicle is virtually brand new, offering you the opportunity to experience the epitome of luxury motoring. Under the hood, the Ghost houses a formidable 6.8L Twin Turbo V12 engine, delivering an awe-inspiring 563 horsepower and a staggering 627 ft-lbs of torque. This powerhouse of an engine ensures that every journey is not just a drive, but an exhilarating experience. Coupled with an 8-Speed Shiftable Automatic transmission, the Ghost glides with seamless precision, offering a ride so smooth and refined, it feels as if you’re floating on a cloud. Whether you're cruising down the highway or navigating through city streets, the Ghost's performance is nothing short of extraordinary, promising an effortless and commanding drive. The exterior of the 2022 Rolls-Royce Ghost is a testament to the brand's commitment to excellence and attention to detail. Its sleek lines and commanding presence are complemented by the iconic Spirit of Ecstasy hood ornament, which stands proudly at the helm, symbolizing the spirit of adventure and the pursuit of excellence. Every inch of the Ghost is crafted with precision, from the meticulously designed grille to the flawless paintwork, ensuring you make a grand entrance wherever you go. Step inside, and you are enveloped in an oasis of luxury and comfort. The interior is a haven of tranquility, where the finest materials come together to create an environment that is both opulent and inviting. Plush leather seats cradle you in comfort, while the exquisite wood veneers and polished metal accents add a touch of sophistication and warmth. The cabin is a sanctuary of silence, thanks to Rolls-Royce's advanced sound insulation technology, allowing you to escape the chaos of the outside world and immerse yourself in a world of serenity. The 2022 Rolls-Royce Ghost is not just about luxury and performance, it is also equipped with a host of advanced features and options that enhance your driving experience. From the state-of-the-art infotainment system that keeps you connected and entertained, to the intuitive driver assistance technologies that ensure your safety and peace of mind, every aspect of the Ghost is designed to cater to your every need. Owning a Rolls-Royce Ghost is not just about possessing a vehicle, it is about embracing a lifestyle of distinction and prestige. This is your chance to own a piece of automotive history, a vehicle that embodies the perfect blend of tradition and innovation. With its low mileage and pristine condition, this 2022 Rolls-Royce Ghost is ready to provide you with years of unparalleled driving pleasure. Don't miss your opportunity to experience the ultimate in luxury and performance. The 2022 Rolls-Royce Ghost is waiting for you, ready to elevate your driving experience to new heights. Contact us today to schedule a test drive and discover why the Ghost is the pinnacle of automotive excellence.

description: Introducing the 2025 BMW i7 eDrive50 Sedan, a remarkable example of modern luxury and cutting-edge technology in the electric vehicle market. This used sedan, with only 4,770 miles on the odometer, epitomizes elegance and efficiency. The exterior of the vehicle is finished in a sleek Alpine White color, offering a clean and sophisticated look that's sure to turn heads. Complementing the luxurious exterior is an exquisite interior adorned in Smoke White, enhancing the overall sense of refinement and comfort. Powered by an all-electric engine, the BMW i7 eDrive50 Sedan is designed for those who desire performance without compromising environmental friendliness. The 2025 BMW i7 eDrive50 Sedan combines innovative electric performance with the luxury and attention to detail BMW is renowned for. Whether you're commuting or embarking on a road trip, this sedan ensures every journey is enjoyable and efficient.

description:
Elevate Your Driving Experience with the Exceptional 2025 Cadillac CT5 V-Series

Introducing the 2025 Cadillac CT5 V-Series, a true masterpiece of automotive engineering that will captivate your senses and redefine your driving dynamics. This sleek and powerful sedan is more than just a vehicle – it's a statement of refined taste and uncompromising performance.

• Super Cruise 1 Package: A hands-free driver assistance system for use on compatible roads, includes Super Cruise, Driver Attention Assist, and a leather-wrapped Super Cruise steering wheel
• Performance Data and Video Recorder
• UltraView Dual Pane Sunroof
• Parking Package: Includes Air Filter, Air Quality Sensor, Rear Camera Mirror, and Hands-Free Decklid Release

Beneath the striking black exterior lies the heart of a true champion – a 6.2L V8 Supercharged engine that delivers exhilarating power and responsiveness. Paired with a 10-speed automatic transmission and rear-wheel drive, this Cadillac CT5 V-Series promises an unparalleled driving experience that will leave you craving more.

Step inside the cabin and you'll be greeted by a world of luxury and sophistication. The Jet Black interior with Jet Black accents and sueded front seatbacks, complemented by the Twenty-Two Carbon Fiber trim, creates an atmosphere of refined elegance. The 16-speaker AKG premium audio system will immerse you in a symphony of sound, while the Google Automotive Services-capable navigation system will guide you effortlessly to your destination.

Comfort and convenience are at the forefront, with features like heated and ventilated front seats, a heated steering wheel, and dual-zone automatic climate control. The Rear Camera Mirror and Hands-Free Decklid Release add to the seamless ownership experience, ensuring you can effortlessly access and maneuver your vehicle.

Safety is paramount in the Cadillac CT5 V-Series, with a comprehensive suite of advanced driver-assistance technologies. From Adaptive Cruise Control and Automatic Emergency Braking to Blind Zone Steering Assist and Reverse Automatic Braking, you can rest assured that you and your passengers are well-protected.

This exceptional 2025 Cadillac CT5 V-Series is a testament to the brand's commitment to delivering uncompromising performance, luxury, and innovation. Experience the thrill of the open road and the confidence of owning a true driver's car. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate why the Cadillac CT5 V-Series is the ultimate choice for the discerning automotive enthusiast.

Discover the epitome of luxury and performance in this stunning 2024 Cadillac XT5 Premium Luxury. This exceptional SUV is a true testament to Cadillac's commitment to craftsmanship and innovation, blending sophisticated design with cutting-edge technology to deliver an unparalleled driving experience.

Boasting a clean CarFax and a one-owner history, this XT5 is a true gem. Adorned in the captivating Stellar Black Metallic exterior, it exudes an elegant and commanding presence on the road. Under the hood, the powerful 3.6L V6 DI VVT engine, paired with a responsive 9-Speed Automatic transmission and Cadillac's renowned All-Wheel Drive system, delivers a thrilling and confident performance, with an impressive fuel efficiency of 18 MPG in the city and 26 MPG on the highway.

Step inside the XT5 Premium Luxury and be captivated by the exquisite attention to detail. The luxurious leather seating surfaces with mini perforated inserts provide unparalleled comfort, while the Tri-Zone Automatic Climate Control ensures everyone on board enjoys their perfect temperature. The Bose Performance Series 14-Speaker System delivers an immersive audio experience, and the intuitive Cadillac User Experience with embedded navigation keeps you connected and informed on the go.

Safety and convenience are also at the forefront of this remarkable SUV. The Automatic Emergency Braking, Front and Rear Park Assist, and HD Rear Vision Camera work in harmony to provide you with added peace of mind on the road. The Wireless Apple CarPlay and Wireless Android Auto integration, along with the Wireless Phone Charging, seamlessly integrate your smartphone, allowing you to stay connected without the hassle of cords.

This 2024 Cadillac XT5 Premium Luxury is a true masterpiece, combining style, performance, and technology in a way that sets a new standard in the luxury SUV segment. Experience the difference for yourself by scheduling a test drive at our showroom today. We're confident that once you get behind the wheel, you'll be captivated by the unparalleled driving experience and exceptional features that make this XT5 a must-have addition to your garage.

  • Adaptive Cruise Control (ACC)
  • 14-Way Comfort Seats with Comfort Memory
  • Storage Package
Convenience
  • Unresponsive driver assistant - a reaction to inaction. Maybe you fell asleep. Maybe you lost consciousness. No matter how it happens, Unresponsive driver assistant works to help lessen the danger when it does. It detects prolonged driver unresponsiveness, automatically bringing the vehicle to a stop and turning on the hazard lights. If equipped, emergency services will also be contacted. Unresponsive driver assistant is safety that never sleeps.
Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
Technology and Telematics
  • Apple CarPlay and Android Auto smart device wireless mirroring
  • Connect Plus incl. wireless Apple CarPlay and wired Android Auto smart device wireless mirroring

Convenience
  • Unresponsive driver assistant - a reaction to inaction. Maybe you fell asleep. Maybe you lost consciousness. No matter how it happens, Unresponsive driver assistant works to help lessen the danger when it does. It detects prolonged driver unresponsiveness, automatically bringing the vehicle to a stop and turning on the hazard lights. If equipped, emergency services will also be contacted. Unresponsive driver assistant is safety that never sleeps.
Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
Technology and Telematics
  • Apple CarPlay and Android Auto smart device wireless mirroring
  • Connect Plus incl. wireless Apple CarPlay and wired Android Auto smart device wireless mirroring

description:
2020 PORSCHE TAYCAN TURBO S

CLIMATE CONTROLLED SEATS, BURMESTER SOUND SYSTEM, PREMIUM PACKAGE, AND MORE!

OVERVIEW
This isn't just an EV. This is a Porsche––and the Taycan Turbo S is proof that performance and razor-sharp driving dynamics didn't die with the internal combustion engine––they just evolved. Dual electric motors deliver a staggering 750 horsepower and up to 774 lb-ft of torque when Launch Control is engaged, propelling the Taycan Turbo S from 0-60 mph in an astonishing 2.4 seconds. Porsche's advanced two-speed rear transmission and all-wheel-drive system ensure relentless acceleration, while offering around 200 miles of range on a full charge. And thanks to its low-slung battery, it doesn't just go fast in a straight line, it corners like a 911 on rails, with grip for days and instant torque vectoring. Step inside and you're greeted with a cockpit that blends Porsche tradition with next-gen tech. From the wraparound digital displays to the 18-way Adaptive Sport Seats, everything is focused, intentional, and driver-first. Some notable added options include heated/ventilated front seats, a Burmester sound system, and ceramic composite brakes. Designed to thrill, this stunning Porsche Taycan Turbo S delivers loads of creature comforts, cutting-edge technology, and the ultimate expression of Porsche engineering in an all-electric form.

Elevate your driving experience with this exceptional 2020 Porsche Taycan Turbo S. This all-electric masterpiece combines the unparalleled performance and craftsmanship Porsche is renowned for, with the cutting-edge technology and eco-friendly efficiency that modern drivers demand.

This Taycan Turbo S delivers an unparalleled driving experience, with its 616 horsepower electric powertrain and all-wheel-drive system providing exhilarating acceleration and precise handling. The sleek, aerodynamic exterior is complemented by a stunning interior that pampers you with premium materials, cutting-edge technology, and thoughtful amenities.

The Taycan Turbo S is a true masterpiece of engineering, combining Porsche's legendary performance heritage with the latest advancements in electric vehicle technology. This 2022 Porsche Panamera Platinum Edition RWD in elegant
Night Blue Metallic is a rare opportunity to own a luxury sport sedan with exceptionally low mileage 32,689 miles below market average. Blending Porsche performance with executive-level refinement, this Panamera delivers both thrilling dynamics and everyday comfort.

Powered by a responsive V6 engine paired with Porsches renowned 8-Speed Porsche Doppelkupplung (PDK) transmission, this rear-wheel-drive Panamera offers seamless acceleration, crisp gear changes, and balanced handling. The adaptive suspension ensures a composed, athletic ride whether cruising the highway or carving through winding roads.

Inside, the cabin reflects Porsches driver-focused luxury. Heated front seats, memory seating, and front dual-zone A/C provide tailored comfort, while the power moonroof enhances the open, airy feel of the interior. The leather steering wheel and leather shift knob add tactile refinement, and the rear 2+1 seating configuration offers added practicality without sacrificing sportiness.

Technology and connectivity are front and center with Porsche Communication Management (PCM), Navigation System, and Apple CarPlay integration. Steering wheel-mounted audio controls keep everything at your fingertips, while remote keyless entry and a power liftgate add everyday convenience.

Safety and driver assistance features include ABS brakes, Electronic Stability Control, Traction Control, Low Tire Pressure Warning, and ParkAssist (Front and Rear) with Surround View, providing confidence in tight spaces and busy traffic conditions.

Completing the look are striking 21 911 Turbo Design wheels, giving this Platinum Edition a commanding stance and unmistakable Porsche presence.

With ultra-low mileage, premium features, and timeless performance, this 2022 Porsche Panamera Platinum Edition is an exceptional sport sedan that perfectly balances luxury, practicality, and driving excitement.


CPO Limited Warranty Coverage: 2 Years/Unlimited Miles Warranty after the expiration of the new vehicle limited warranty or from the date of sale if the new vehicle limited warranty has expired. Experience high-performance luxury with this 2022 Cadillac CT5-V Blackwing, a meticulously maintained sport sedan located in Naples, FL. Powered by a potent 6.2L V8 gasoline engine and rear-wheel drive, this Cadillac CT5 Blackwing delivers exhilarating acceleration, precise handling, and a commanding exhaust note that enthusiasts demand. With only 38,324 miles, this example pairs performance with practicality for weekend thrills or daily driving. This vehicle comes with a CARFAX Clean Report, confirming a transparent history and added peace of mind. Inside, enjoy modern connectivity and convenience features including Apple CarPlay for seamless smartphone integration, Remote Start for quick climate control, Adaptive Cruise Control for relaxed highway driving, and a Back-Up Camera to assist with parking and safety. The interior is crafted with driver-focused ergonomics and premium materials that elevate every commute. Situated in Naples, FL, this Cadillac CT5 Blackwing is competitively priced and represents the best value available — offering top-tier performance at the best price in the area. Whether you're seeking a track-capable sedan or a refined high-performance daily driver, this Cadillac combines raw power and advanced technology in a refined package. Schedule a test drive today in Naples to feel the 6.2L V8 and experience why this Cadillac CT5 Blackwing stands out among performance sedans.

Equipment
The leather seats in this vehicle are a must for buyers looking for comfort, durability, and style. This model comes equipped with Android Auto for seamless smartphone integration on the road. Never get into a cold vehicle again with the remote start feature on it. The installed navigation system will keep you on the right path. Step into a world of possibilities with this stunning MANUFAKTUR Diamond White 2022 Mercedes-Benz S-Class. Its aerodynamic design isn’t just for looks—it’s built to move you forward with style and efficiency. Under the hood, a reliable 4.0L V8 delivers performance you can count on for the long haul.

Loaded with smart features such as 3D Technology Package (3D Instrument Cluster and MBUX Augmented Reality Head-Up Display), AMG® Line Package (AMG® Floor Mats and AMG® Line Exterior (772)), Sport Package Code, Warmth & Comfort Launch Package (Heated Front Armrests, Heated Rear Armrests, Heated Steering Wheel, Memory Rear Seats, Power Rear Seats, Rear Seat Heating, and Ventilated Rear Seats), 4.5 Degree Rear Axle Steering, Adaptive Rear Lighting, Apple CarPlay®/Android Auto®, Auto High-beam Headlights, Auto-leveling suspension, Automatic temperature control, Brake assist, Delay-off headlights, Electronic Stability Control, Exterior Parking Camera Rear, Front dual zone A/C, Garage door transmitter: HomeLink, Heated door mirrors, HVAC memory, Memory seat, Navigation System, Power moonroof: Panorama, Rear fog lights, Remote keyless entry, Steering wheel memory, Turn signal indicator mirrors, and Wheels: 21" x 9J Fr & 21" x 10J Rr AMG® V-Multispoke, this S-Class is more than a car—it’s your passport to freedom. From daily commutes to weekend getaways, it’s spacious enough to carry everything you need (and then some).

Think the pictures look good? Just wait until you see it in your driveway.

Fuel your drive. Embrace the journey. Your S-Class is waiting.


Experience the McGrath Legacy - 60+ Years of Driving Excellence

With four generations dedicated to delivering exceptional automotive experiences, the McGrath family has proudly served Chicagoland drivers for more than six decades. At McGrath BMW of Elmhurst, we're not just here to sell you your next BMW, we're here to build a lasting relationship by helping you maintain your vehicle and stay confidently on the road for years to come.

As Chicagolands oldest BMW dealership, we’re honored to serve customers across Elmhurst and surrounding suburbs such as Oak Brook, Butterfield, Wheaton, Glen Ellyn, Lombard, Villa Park, Glendale Heights, Carol Stream, Bloomingdale, Medinah, Roselle, Itasca, Addison, Wood Dale Bensenville, Franklin Park, Northlake, Berkeley, Bellwood, Elk Grove Village, La Grange Park and beyond. Every guest who walks through our door is treated like family, and it shows in everything we do.

Discover a car-buying experience that goes beyond expectations - where legendary service meets the ultimate driving machine.

Call us today at (844) 717-6437 to schedule your exclusive VIP test drive and take your experience to the next level.

description:
Mercedes-Benz of Palm Springs is delighted to showcase, this Certified Pre-Owned 2022 Mercedes-Benz S 580 Sedan. Dressed in an elegant Black exterior and paired with a Black Exclusive Nappa Leather interior, with just 16,051 miles to its name, this flagship luxury sedan exemplifies the pinnacle of Mercedes-Benz engineering, comfort, and innovation.

The S-Class has long stood as the benchmark for full-size luxury sedans, and this S 580 is no exception. Its commanding presence is enhanced by refined exterior design cues, advanced LED lighting, and a sophisticated stance that reflects timeless elegance. With features such as AIRMATIC air suspension, Surround View Camera, and Active Distance Assist DISTRONIC, this sedan delivers both confidence and composure on every drive.


Step inside and experience a sanctuary of modern luxury. The Black Exclusive Nappa Leather interior surrounds you with exquisite craftsmanship, while the expansive MBUX multimedia system, Burmester High-End 4D Surround Sound System, and multi-color ambient lighting create an immersive driving environment. Heated and ventilated multi-contour seats with massage, along with advanced comfort and assistance technologies, ensure every journey is effortless and indulgent.

Engine and Performance: Powering this remarkable sedan is a formidable 4.0-liter V8 biturbo engine with EQ Boost, producing an impressive 496 horsepower and 516 lb-ft of torque. Paired with the refined 9G-TRONIC 9-speed automatic transmission, the S 580 delivers seamless acceleration, exceptional smoothness, and commanding performance, all while maintaining the quiet sophistication expected of the S-Class.

Key Features:

• Driver Assistance Package: A comprehensive suite of advanced safety and semi-autonomous driving technologies designed to enhance confidence and peace of mind.

• Executive Rear Seat & Rear Seat Comfort Packages: Elevating rear passenger comfort with enhanced seating, climate control, and luxury amenities.

• Burmester High-End 4D Surround Sound System: An audiophile-grade system delivering breathtaking sound quality throughout the cabin.

• MBUX Navigation Premium & Augmented Reality: Advanced navigation with real-time visuals for intuitive guidance.

• AIRMATIC Suspension: Automatically adapts to road conditions for an exceptionally smooth and composed ride.

• Panorama Sunroof: Floods the cabin with natural light, enhancing the open and airy feel of the interior.

This 2022 Mercedes-Benz S 580 Sedan is far more than just a vehicle, it is a statement of prestige, innovation, and uncompromising luxury. Available now at Mercedes-Benz of Palm Springs, it offers an extraordinary opportunity to experience the very best of the S-Class legacy.



Mercedes-Benz of Palm Springs is a member of the indiGO Auto Group. Our dealership features a beautiful showroom, fully staffed factory certified service center, parts department, finance department, detail department, and accessories boutique. Allow us to also help arrange transportation of your new car directly to your home anywhere in the world. Trade-in proposals are always welcome. If you like this vehicle and have questions, simply call, email, or drop by our location. We invite you to Activate Your Ownership with us today!

description:
Elevate your driving experience with this exceptional 2022 BMW M5 Base Executive Package. This high-performance sedan combines unparalleled power, refined luxury, and cutting-edge technology, making it the ultimate choice for the discerning automotive enthusiast.

- Competition Package: Includes extended Shadowline trim, M Sport exhaust system, additional 17 HP, black chrome tailpipes, lowered sport suspension, and extended black high-gloss design elements.
- Executive Package: Offers front ventilated seats, active park distance control, soft-close automatic doors, drive recorder, surround view with 3D view, rear view camera, front massaging seats, power rear sunshade, and front and rear heated seats.
- Driving Assistance Professional Package: Provides active driving assistant pro, active cruise control with stop and go, active lane keeping assistant with side collision avoidance, traffic jam assistant, evasion aid, and cross-traffic alert front.
- Stunning 20-inch M Y-spoke forged bi-color wheels with performance tires and the Individual Piano Black Finish Trim exude a bold, aggressive presence.

Beneath the sculpted exterior lies a potent 4.4L V8 Turbocharged engine that delivers an exhilarating 600 horsepower, propelling this M5 from 0 to 60 mph in a mere 3.2 seconds. The 8-speed automatic sport transmission and xDrive all-wheel-drive system ensure seamless power delivery and exceptional handling, making this M5 a true driver's delight.

The luxurious cabin is adorned with Silverstone Merino leather upholstery and features a wealth of premium amenities, including a Harman Kardon surround sound system, wireless charging, and a comprehensive suite of advanced safety and connectivity technologies. The Executive Package further enhances the experience with front massaging seats, a head-up display, and a surround-view camera system.

This 2022 BMW M5 Base Executive Package is a testament to the brand's commitment to engineering excellence and uncompromising performance. Whether you're seeking a thrilling daily driver or a capable weekend warrior, this M5 is poised to exceed your expectations and redefine your driving experience.

Proudly Serving Maricopa, Tempe, Chandler, Surprise, Phoenix, Scottsdale, Tucson, Mesa, Flagstaff, Prescott, Sedona, Payson. Please call for availability. There are many new arrivals daily that may not show online yet!

Marked by excellent quality and features with unmistakable refined leather interior that added value and class to the Subaru Forester 2.5i Limited. More information about the 2014 Subaru Forester: The Subaru Forester has always been a very nice compromise between the practicality of a small hatchback or station wagon and the capabilities of an SUV. Though it can't off-road like some of the more serious SUVs out there, the Forester does at least come standard with all-wheel-drive, unlike most of its competition. Though base model Foresters perform similarly to competitors from Ford and Mazda, turbocharged versions offers significantly more power, resulting in sprightly performance. On-road handling is also a step above what is generally offered in this segment. The Forester starts at just under $22,000. description: Step into the future of electric performance with the 2025 BMW i4 eDrive40, a sleek all-electric luxury sport sedan that blends exhilarating driving dynamics with advanced technology and refined comfort. Designed for drivers who want efficiency without sacrificing excitement, the BMW i4 delivers a powerful and engaging electric driving experience.The BMW i4 eDrive40 features an advanced electric drivetrain that provides instant torque, smooth acceleration, and a quiet, refined ride. Rear-wheel drive dynamics deliver a balanced and responsive feel, while precision engineering ensures confident handling on city streets and open highways alike. This electric BMW proves that performance and sustainability can go hand in hand.Inside, the 2025 BMW i4 eDrive40 offers a modern, driver-focused cabin crafted with premium materials and innovative design. Advanced BMW technology enhances every journey with a sweeping digital display, intuitive controls, and seamless connectivity that keeps you informed and entertained. Intelligent driver assistance features add an extra layer of confidence, supporting comfort, safety, and convenience.Despite its sporty profile, the BMW i4 provides impressive practicality with comfortable seating and versatile cargo space, making it ideal for daily commuting and longer trips. The electric powertrain delivers smooth, efficient performance while maintaining the engaging character BMW drivers expect.With its bold styling, athletic stance, and unmistakable BMW presence, the 2025 BMW i4 eDrive40 stands out as a forward-thinking luxury sedan. Discover the epitome of performance and luxury in the all-new 2025 Audi S5 3.0T Prestige quattro. This stunning coupe is a true testament to Audi's engineering excellence, blending exhilarating power, refined sophistication, and cutting-edge technology.

• One Owner Car Fax

Powered by a potent 3.0L TFSI engine and paired with a lightning-fast 7-Speed Automatic S tronic transmission, the S5 delivers an exceptional driving experience. With the legendary quattro all-wheel-drive system, you'll enjoy unparalleled traction and control, no matter the conditions.

This meticulously maintained S5 boasts a sleek Black exterior, complemented by a stunning interior that combines premium Nappa leather and Dinamica seating surfaces. Elevate your driving experience with the Prestige Package, which includes a suite of advanced features, such as the cutting-edge Navigation System, the immersive Bang & Olufsen Sound System, and the convenience of a Panoramic Glass Roof with Variable Light Control.

Certified as a one-owner vehicle with a clean CARFAX report, this S5 has been meticulously cared for and is ready to provide you with years of exceptional performance and luxury. Discover the thrill of driving the all-new Audi S5 3.0T Prestige quattro and experience the pinnacle of German engineering.

With a city fuel economy of 19 MPG and a highway rating of 28 MPG, this S5 delivers impressive efficiency without sacrificing power. Prepare to be captivated by the dynamic handling, precise steering, and responsive acceleration that make this Audi a true driver's delight.

This 2025 Mercedes-Benz C-Class C 300 is a remarkable opportunity for the savvy driver seeking a premium driving experience. With only 3,929 miles on the odometer, this vehicle has been meticulously maintained and is ready to provide you with the exceptional performance and luxurious features you expect from the Mercedes-Benz brand.

• Panorama Roof
• Burmester® 3D Surround Sound System
• Perforated Brake Discs
• PRE-SAFE® PLUS
• GUARD 360
• Active Lane Change Assist
• DISTRONIC Plus® with Steering Assist and Stop and Go Assist

• AMG® Body Styling
• AMG® Line Exterior
• Sport Suspension with Sport Steering System
• Star Grille
• Active Speed Limit Assist

• Enhanced Ambient Light
• Illuminated Door Sills
• MB Navigation
• MB-Tex Dashboard

• Surround View

Powered by a 2.0L I4 Turbocharged engine and equipped with a 9-Speed Automatic transmission, this C-Class delivers an impressive balance of power and efficiency, with an EPA-estimated 25 MPG in the city and 35 MPG on the highway. The AMG® Line with Night Package, Driver Assistance Package, Driver Assistance Package Plus, Exclusive Trim Package, and Night Package further elevate the driving experience, providing a dynamic and refined ride.

The stunning Black exterior complements the well-appointed interior, which features premium MB-Tex upholstery, heated and ventilated front seats, and a Burmester® 3D Surround Sound System. The advanced driver-assistance technologies, including Active Blind Spot Assist, Evasive Steering Assist, and PRE-SAFE® Brake with Pedestrian Recognition, ensure your safety and peace of mind on the road.

This 2025 Mercedes-Benz C-Class C 300 is a true testament to the brand's commitment to excellence. With its exceptional performance, advanced features, and impeccable condition, it is the perfect choice for the discerning driver who demands the very best. description:
This 2025 E 350 4MATIC in Polar White with a Black MB-Tex interior delivers a refined blend of luxury, technology, and confident all-weather performance. The MBUX Superscreen Package transforms the cabin with a striking digital display that includes a front passenger screen, selfie and video camera, and an intuitive multimedia interface. Pinnacle Trim elevates the experience further with a head-up display, illuminated radiator grille, Burmester surround sound system, enhanced ambient lighting, and heat and noise insulating glass for a quieter, more immersive drive.

Advanced safety and convenience are at the forefront thanks to the Driver Assistance Package, offering Active Distance Assist DISTRONIC, Active Steering Assist, Active Lane Change Assist, and Pre-Safe Impulse Side protection. The DIGITAL LIGHT Package enhances visibility with intelligent lighting and projection functionality, while the Multicontour Seating Package adds massaging, heated, and ventilated front seats, rapid heating, heated armrests, and ENERGIZING Comfort features for exceptional long-distance comfort. Finished with 19-inch AMG twin five-spoke wheels, a Nappa leather steering wheel, and subtle exterior accents, this E-Class is an elegant, technology-forward sedan designed for both daily commuting and long highway drives.
