description:
Elevate your driving experience with this exquisite 2025 Audi S5 3.0T Prestige quattro. Meticulously maintained and boasting a mere 2,685 miles, this captivating sports coupe is poised to exceed your every expectation.

Packed with an impressive array of premium features, this S5 is a true standout. Key highlights include:

• Custom features: Questions text or call Eric Hedges 256.529.2280
• Edition One, LED Interior Lighting Pro Package, Prestige Package
• Navigation system: MMI Navigation plus, Bang & Olufsen Sound System with 3D Sound, Head-Up Display, Heated Rear Seats, Heated Steering Wheel with Hands-on Detection, Panoramic Glass with Variable Light Control, Headlight Washers, Adaptive Cruise Assist, and much more

Powered by a potent 3.0L TFSI engine and quattro all-wheel drive, the S5 delivers an exhilarating driving experience with exceptional fuel efficiency, achieving an impressive 19 MPG in the city and 28 MPG on the highway.

The exterior is finished in a stunning Gray, accentuated by a host of premium design elements, including Matrix Design LED Headlights, Dark Chrome Exhaust Tips, and Liquid Chrome Air Intakes and Rear Diffusors. The interior is equally impressive, featuring Fine Nappa/Pearl Nappa Leather Seating Surfaces, Front Sport Seats Plus with Ventilation and Massage, and a striking Vanadium Look interior trim.

This S5 is a true testament to Audi's commitment to excellence, blending breathtaking performance, cutting-edge technology, and unparalleled luxury. Experience the difference for yourself and schedule a test drive today.

Our Best Price Guarantee
We use real-time market data to ensure our online prices are among the most aggressive within a 300-mile radius. Unlike many competitors or private sellers, every pre-owned vehicle in our inventory undergoes a rigorous professional servicing before it reaches the lot. To provide these deep discounts, our advertised price is inclusive of a $2,000 finance incentive for customers who use one of our preferred lenders. We welcome cash purchases, however, please note that the selling price will be higher to account for the loss of the finance incentive.

Safety and Security
  • The vehicle constantly monitors the roadway in front of the vehicle and identifies and tracks pedestrians on an interior display. If the system determines a likely impact, it will automatically take preventative steps to avoid hitting the pedestrian.
  • The vehicle is equipped with a camera that displays an image of the area behind the vehicle on an interior display.
  • An active lane departure system alerts the driver of unintended movement of the vehicle out of a designated traffic lane and automatically maintains the vehicle's position within that lane.
  • The vehicle is equipped with a system that senses, and then prepares, the vehicle and/or occupants, for an impending rear collision.
Technology and Telematics

Step into the future of driving with the 2020 Porsche Taycan, where electrifying performance meets the laid-back luxury of Northern Californias vibrant lifestyle. As you settle into the quad bucket seats wrapped in Olea Club leather, the world outside fades away, leaving only the promise of exhilarating journeys ahead. The expansive glass panoramic roof floods the cabin with natural light, creating an airy atmosphere that invites you to connect with the vibrant Bay Area skyline above. With the Premium Package, every detail is designed for your comfort and convenience, from the advanced 4-zone climate control to the heated steering wheel that wraps you in warmth on brisk mornings. The Porsche InnoDrive with Adaptive Cruise Control ensures a smooth ride, allowing you to navigate with confidence while the Surround View camera system provides peace of mind as you maneuver through tight spaces. The Sport Chrono Package adds a thrilling edge to your drive, delivering precision and responsiveness that only Porsche can offer. With the power liftgate and all-wheel drive, loading up for a weekend getaway is effortless, making this Taycan the perfect companion for both daily commutes and spontaneous adventures. This is not just a car, its a statement of innovation and performance, crafted for those who demand the extraordinary. Ready to redefine your driving experience? Visit us today and let the Porsche Taycan take you on a journey where luxury meets electric performance.According to CARFAXs Vehicle History Report, this car had only one previous owner and is well-maintained (regular oil changes, general maintenance)!!

description:
The 2020 BMW M5 Competition offers an unrivaled fusion of executive luxury and race-bred performance, finished in a sophisticated Rhodonite Silver Metallic exterior. Powered by the hand-built 4.4L twin-turbocharged S63 V8 engine delivering a breathtaking 617 horsepower and 553 lb-ft of torque, this super-sedan achieves 0-60 mph in a staggering 3.1 seconds through its 8-speed M STEPTRONIC transmission and the intelligent M xDrive all-wheel-drive system, which offers rear-biased dynamics and a dedicated 2WD mode for supreme control on any surface.

The track-focused Competition package outfits the M5 with aggressive 20-inch M Light-Alloy wheels, high-performance tires, and an M Sport exhaust system for an unmistakable soundtrack. Inside, you'll find full Merino leather upholstery with M-specific bolstering, a carbon fiber trim interior, and an Alcantara-wrapped steering wheel with shift paddles. The driver-centric cockpit features illuminated M front seats with massage functions, a head-up display, and a premium 16-speaker Harman Kardon surround sound system for every journey, from the track to the autobahn.

Cutting-edge technology features include the latest iDrive 7.0 system with a 12.3-inch digital instrument cluster and a 10.25-inch touchscreen, wireless Apple CarPlay and Android Auto integration, and gesture control. The M5 Competition also boasts an Adaptive M Suspension Professional and BMW's comprehensive Driving Assistant Professional suite for ultimate precision and confidence at any speed.

Engineered for domination, this M5 Competition achieves an EPA-estimated 15 MPG city/21 MPG highway, a figure rendered trivial by its status as one of the most capable performance sedans ever built.

Experience Hassle-Free Shopping at Ames Ford Lincoln:

- Premium Quality Assurance: Rest assured with our meticulous vehicle inspections and reconditioning, averaging over $2,000 per car, ensuring your peace of mind when purchasing a pre-owned vehicle. That's why they're all backed by our 7-Day Like it or Return it Money Back Guarantee.

- Non-commissioned Sales Consultants: Means no pushy sales tactics, just friendly professionals to help you find the best car for your needs.

- Unmatched Transparency: Prior to your purchase, gain full visibility into the service history of the vehicle, ensuring complete transparency and confidence in your decision.

- Our Best Price Upfront: We recognize the extensive research done by shoppers, hence we offer highly competitive prices online to match your needs and expectations.

- Express Checkout for Time Efficiency: Streamline your purchase process by completing most of the deal remotely, whether from the comfort of your workplace or home, saving you valuable time.

Our powerful 2021 BMW M Series M5 Sedan in striking Frozen Bluestone Metallic is a true icon of premium performance, delivering exhilarating twin-turbo V8 power, precision handling, and bold M styling for an elite driving experience. Motivated by a Twin-TurboCharged 4.4 Liter V8 that offers 600hp to an 8 Speed M Steptronic Automatic transmission for rocket-like runs to 60mph in a brief 3.2 seconds. This All Wheel Drive sports sedan also moves with M-tuned suspension and braking systems for track-friendly handling, and it returns nearly 21mpg on the highway. Aerodynamic and sophisticated, our M5 emphasizes its athletic spirit with adaptive LED headlamps, a bold body kit, and alloy wheels. Enthusiasts love the comfort of our M5 cabin, which shows off heated Merino leather power front seats, an M sports heated steering wheel, automatic climate control, distinctive Aluminum Carbon Structure trim, and more Merino leather on the dash. A digital driver display, central touchscreen, full-color navigation, Apple CarPlay® compatibility, Bluetooth®, voice control, no-touch gesture control, and Harman Kardon surround-sound audio help keep you connected as you go. BMW's intelligent safety systems promote peace of mind with automatic braking, blind-spot monitoring, a rearview camera, lane-departure warning, pedestrian detection, and more. Drive our M5, and you'll discover a terrific machine that makes other sedans seem tame! Save this Page and Call for Availability. description:
2021 Mercedes-Benz S-Class S 580 4MATIC

VIN: W1K6G7GB4MA034342
Body Style: Full-Size Luxury Sedan
Drivetrain: 4MATIC All-Wheel Drive
Transmission: 9-Speed Automatic
Engine: Twin-Turbocharged 4.0 L V8 with 48-Volt Mild-Hybrid System (~496 hp & 516 lb-ft)
Seating: 5 Passengers
Assembly: Germany

Vehicle Overview

The 2021 Mercedes-Benz S-Class S 580 4MATIC is the definitive expression of luxury automotive engineering combining formidable performance, cutting-edge comfort, and advanced technology into an elegant executive sedan. With its powerful twin-turbo V8 and all-wheel-drive traction, it delivers effortless acceleration while maintaining the refined ride quality S-Class is famed for.

Performance & Power

Twin-Turbo 4.0 L V8 Engine: Produces approximately 496 hp and 516 lb-ft of torque for confident, smooth acceleration.

48-Volt Mild Hybrid System (EQ Boost): Enhances responsiveness and efficiency via electric torque assist.

0-60 mph in ~4.4 seconds: A surprising sprint for a flagship luxury sedan. ([turn0search4][turn0search6])

4MATIC All-Wheel Drive: Balanced traction and composed handling in all weather conditions. ([turn0search1])

Air Suspension & Optional Rear-Axle Steering: Advanced suspension systems deliver a silky-smooth ride with responsive agility for a car of its size.

Luxury Interior & Features

The 2021 S580 cabin wraps passengers in premium materials and thoughtful design:

Opulent Leather Upholstery & Wood Trim: Quiet, elegant finishes throughout.

Generous Passenger Space: A long wheelbase for exceptional front and rear room.

Advanced Infotainment: Dual widescreen displays with navigation, smartphone integration, and intuitive controls.

Comfort Enhancements: Available heated/ventilated seats, massage functions, panoramic roof, soft-close doors, and ambient lighting elevate the driving experience.

Technology & Safety:

Mercedes-Benz equips the S-Class with a suite of driver-assistance systems and high-tech features (equipment varies by vehicle), which often includes:

Adaptive Cruise Control & Lane-Keep Assist

Active Brake Assist & Blind-Spot Monitoring

Head-Up Display & Augmented-Reality Navigation (optional)

Multi-Zone Climate Control & Executive Rear Seat Options
These systems help enhance safety, comfort, and convenience for every journey.



The 2021 Mercedes-Benz S-Class S 580 4MATIC remains one of the most prestigious full-size sedans on the road a benchmark of luxury, performance, and innovation. Its potent V8, refined ride, and upscale cabin make it ideal for discerning drivers who value executive style and cutting-edge automotive technology.

This 2018 Mercedes-Benz S-Class AMG S 63 has a Anthracite Blue Metallic exterior and an Mahogany/Silk Beige interior color. 35,799 miles. stock number A20821B. You can connect with us by calling (704) 535-8800. No Accidents! Important Package and Feature Information Driver Assistance Package
    Driver Assistance Package ($2,250 value)
    • DISTRONIC Plus
    • DISTRONIC PLUS with Steering Assist
    • Speed Limit Assist
    • Automatic Speed Takeover
    • Active Lane Change Assist
    • Extended Restart by Stop and Go
    • Route Based Speed Adaptation
    Safety and Security
    • Night vision - Lift the veil of darkness. We've all been there, it's dark, and suddenly something appears out of nowhere in the road! With this safety feature, the night no longer holds unpleasant surprises. Working in combination with the headlights, night vision uses infrared technology to detect obstacles in the dark and show them on your display screen. Night vision makes for a safer drive between dusk and dawn.
    • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
    • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
    • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
    Technology and Telematics
    • Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road.

This is not just a luxury sedan—it’s a statement of dominance. The 2018 Cadillac CTS-V is where handcrafted luxury collides with supercar-level performance, and this example, finished in Crystal White Tricoat over a Jet Black interior, is a breathtaking expression of Cadillac’s most uncompromising engineering. Under the sculpted hood lives one of the greatest engines ever fitted to a four-door sedan: the hand-built 6.2L supercharged V8, delivering a staggering 640 horsepower and 630 lb-ft of torque. Paired with a lightning-fast 8-speed automatic transmission and rear-wheel drive, the CTS-V launches from 0–60 mph in just 3.6 seconds, while still cruising with refinement and authority. V-Series Performance Engineering 6.2L Supercharged V8 (LT4) – hand-assembled for maximum power and reliability 640 HP / 630 lb-ft of torque 8-speed performance automatic transmission with paddle shifters Magnetic Ride Control – continuously adapts suspension for razor-sharp handling or supple comfort Electronic Limited-Slip Differential for exceptional grip and corner exit traction Red Brembo® performance brake calipers delivering immense stopping power and unmistakable presence This CTS-V doesn’t just accelerate—it dominates corners, devours straights, and stops with absolute confidence. Recaro Performance Seats The cabin is anchored by factory Recaro® performance seats, designed to hold you firmly in place under hard acceleration and high-G cornering: Aggressive bolstering for track-level support Premium materials that balance race-inspired design with Cadillac refinement Performance Data & Video Recorder Turn every drive into a performance event: Records video, audio, speed, braking, steering input, and g-forces Perfect for track days or analyzing spirited drives A rare and highly desirable feature that showcases the CTS-V’s motorsport DNA Carbon Fiber Package Subtle, purposeful, and unmistakably aggressive: Carbon fiber accents that reduce weight and elevate visual impact Reinforces the CTS-V’s track-ready identity Luxury Package Performance doesn’t come at the expense of comfort: Premium materials throughout the cabin Heated and ventilated seating elements (where equipped) Refined fit and finish that rivals European performance sedans This is a car that can attack apexes in the morning and arrive at a five-star dinner in the evening. Advanced Security Package Peace of mind, engineered: Enhanced vehicle protection systems Anti-theft and monitoring technology designed to safeguard this high-performance machine Battery Protection Package Ensures long-term electrical health and reliability—especially valuable in a performance vehicle with advanced electronics and data systems. Power Sunroof Open the cabin to natural light and fresh air, adding an extra layer of enjoyment whether cruising or carving canyon roads. Exterior & Presence Crystal White Tricoat highlights the CTS-V’s aggressive body lines and wide stance Subtle V-Series badging signals serious performance to those who know Red Brembo calipers add a bold contrast and unmistakable motorsport flair The Verdict With 73,532 miles, this 2018 Cadillac CTS-V remains a modern performance icon—a sedan capable of embarrassing supercars while surrounding you in luxury, technology, and unmistakable American confidence. Rarely do cars blend this level of power, precision, comfort, and presence into one unforgettable experience.. description:
Cavallino Rosso St. Louis is proud to present this **2019 Mercedes-Benz AMG E 63 S 4MATIC+ Sedan**, recently traded in and now available for sale. With its **Obsidian Black Metallic exterior** and **Black Exclusive Nappa Leather interior**, this powerful luxury sedan delivers the perfect balance of performance, technology, and refinement.


Performance: Under the hood lies a handcrafted **4.0L Biturbo V8 engine**, producing an incredible **603 horsepower** and **627 lb-ft of torque**, paired to a **9-speed AMG SPEEDSHIFT MCT transmission**. This AWD super sedan rockets from 0 to 60 mph in just about **3.3 seconds**, delivering a thrilling driving experience. AMG Performance 4MATIC+ with **electro-mechanical limited slip differential**, **Air Body Control Suspension**, and the **AMG Performance Exhaust System** provide dynamic handling and engaging exhaust notes.

AMG E 63 S 4MATIC+ Sedan
Obsidian Black Metallic Exterior
Black AMG Exclusive Nappa Leather Upholstery
AMG Performance Exhaust System
20" AMG Forged Cross-Spoke Wheels w/Grey Accents
Panorama Roof
Warmth & Comfort Package
Driver Assistance Package
Exterior Lighting Package
Active Front Seats Package w/Massage Feature
Heated Rear Seats
Metal Weave Interior Trim
Comfort Box
AMG Nappa Leather Performance Steering Wheel
Pre-Wiring for Rear Seat Entertainment & Comfort Adapter
Wheel Locking Bolts
Black Headliner
603 Horsepower/627 lb-ft Torque
060 MPH in ~3.3 Seconds
Original MSRP: $118,735


This 2019 Mercedes-Benz AMG E 63 S represents an outstanding opportunity to own a high-performance luxury sedan with tasteful options and a stunning color combination. Now available at Cavallino Rosso St. Louis.

Official Ferrari Dealer Cavallino Rosso St. Louis, located at 3000 S Hanley Road in St. Louis, Missouri, is your gateway to the world of high-performance Ferraris and luxury vehicles. Cavallino Rosso St. Louis is the premier destination for enthusiasts seeking the iconic luxury and performance synonymous with the Ferrari brand. Cavallino Rosso has the capability to sell and deliver vehicles to customers throughout the United States. All vehicles are fully inspected and serviced in our state of the art Ferrari Service Center.

As a member of the Indigo Auto Group, Cavallino Rosso embodies the same commitment to excellence and passion for luxury vehicles that define the group as a whole.

To get the most accurate and up-to-date information regarding Cavallino Rosso St. Louis's services and vehicle availability please visit our official website at cavallinorossostlouis.com or call us directly at 314-626-9547.

description: This Graphite Gray 2022 Mercedes-Benz S-Class S 500 Sedan represents the highest level of automotive luxury and innovation. Powered by a refined 3.0L V6 Turbocharged engine and a seamless 9-speed automatic transmission, it delivers power with incredible smoothness. The 4MATIC all-wheel drive system ensures you have maximum grip and stability, providing a confident ride in any weather. As the flagship of the Mercedes-Benz lineup, this S 500 Sedan offers a level of prestige and comfort that few other vehicles can match.The interior of this S 500 Sedan is a true masterpiece of design, featuring supple leather upholstery and genuine wood accents on the dashboard and doors. You and your passengers will enjoy ultimate comfort with heated and ventilated front seats, while the Panorama power moonroof makes the cabin feel open and airy. Every detail is focused on relaxation, including the 4-position memory seats and dual-zone automatic climate control. Whether you are driving or being driven, this sedan provides a quiet and peaceful sanctuary from the outside world.Technology in this S 500 Sedan is simply breathtaking, highlighted by the 3D Technology Package. It includes a 3D Instrument Cluster that provides a lifelike display of your driving data and an MBUX Augmented Reality Head-Up Display that projects navigation directions directly onto your view of the road. The Burmester 3D Surround Sound System fills the cabin with concert-quality audio, making every song an experience. With smartphone integration and the advanced MBUX navigation system, you are always connected and on the right path.The driving experience is further enhanced by the revolutionary E-ACTIVE BODY CONTROL and adaptive suspension. This system reads the road ahead and adjusts the auto-leveling suspension in real time to glide over bumps as if they were not even there. Safety is also a top priority, with features like auto high-beam headlights, rain-sensing wipers, and turn signal indicator mirrors. The exterior parking camera and various sensors make navigating this large, elegant sedan effortless in any parking situation.This Graphite Gray S 500 Sedan is a CARFAX One-Owner vehicle and has earned the Mercedes-Benz Certified Pre-Owned status. This means it has passed a strict 165-point inspection to ensure it meets the highest possible standards. It is a vehicle built for those who refuse to settle for anything less than the best in terms of safety, style, and futuristic technology. If you are looking for the ultimate executive transport, this S 500 Sedan is ready for you.Check Availability Now or Call 727-306-9453.727-306-9453 Our Mercedes-Benz Factory Certification program is a curation of the very best Pre-Owned Mercedes-Benz vehicles available. Each and every one has passed a rigorous, 162-point Factory inspection and been completely reconditioned inside and out. All services and maintenance are up to date, including tires, brakes, belts, hoses and all fluids. Comes with 24/7 Roadside Assistance, Trip-Interruption Coverage, CARFAX service records available.*Burmester is a registered trademark of Burmester Audiosysteme GmbH, Berlin, Germany.

Our Accident Free, One Owner, Certified Pre-Owned, Low Mileage 2026 Cadillac CT5-V Sedan can deliver an adrenaline rush backed by refined comfort in Black Raven! Motivated by a Twin-TurboCharged 3.0 Liter V6 delivering 360hp to a paddle-shifted 10 Speed Automatic transmission for aggressive acceleration. Brembo brakes, Magnetic Ride Control, and a limited-slip differential help you power through twisty roads, and Rear Wheel Drive sedan scores nearly 27mpg on the highway with a sleek and purposeful design. Premium Cadillac details include LED lighting, quad exhaust outlets, 19-inch wheels, a rear spoiler, bold rocker extensions, and heated power mirrors.

Move to our CT5-V cockpit, and youll discover high-end features for high-performance driving with heated Intelux power front sport seats, a heated power-adjustable steering wheel, dual-zone automatic climate control, alloy pedals, and a high-tech 33-inch infotainment display. Intuitive and easy to use, it helps you enjoy Google Built-in compatibility, Apple CarPlayÂ®, WiFi compatibility, Android AutoÂ®, BluetoothÂ®, wireless charging, and a 15-speaker AKG audio system.

Hands-free driving is here, thanks to Cadillac Super Cruise compatibility, and its complemented by advanced passenger protection with front/rear auto braking, blind-spot monitoring, HD surround vision, automatic parking assistance, lane-keeping assistance, and more. Masterful craftsmanship makes the difference in our CT5-V! Save this Page and Call for Availability. We Know You Will Enjoy Your Lithia Suburban Cadillac of Plymouth Test Drive Towards Ownership!

MP3 Player, Remote Trunk Release, Keyless Entry, Steering Wheel Controls, Child Safety Locks. Boasting a stunning array of premium features, this CLA 250 is a true standout. Key highlights include:

Whether you're navigating the urban landscape or exploring open roads, this 2026 BMW 3 Series 330i is the perfect companion. Its exceptional performance, advanced technology, and luxurious appointments make it a standout in its class. We invite you to experience the power and refinement of this exceptional vehicle firsthand. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate why this 3 Series is the perfect choice for the discerning driver.

Discover the epitome of sophistication and performance in the 2026 Toyota Crown Nightshade. This captivating sedan is a masterful blend of cutting-edge technology, uncompromising comfort, and head-turning style.

- Illuminated Door Sills (TMS)
- All Weather Floor Liner & Cargo Tray (TMS)
- Mudguards (TMS)
- Navigation system: Dynamic Navigation (3-year trial)
- 11 Speakers
- AM/FM radio: SiriusXM
- 12.3" Toyota Audio Multimedia
- Automatic temperature control
- Memory seat
- Power driver seat
- Four wheel independent suspension
- ABS brakes
- Emergency communication system: Safety Connect (5-year minimum)
- Exterior Parking Camera Rear
- Auto High-beam Headlights

The Crown Nightshade's striking black exterior exudes a commanding presence, while its spacious and well-appointed interior pampers you with unparalleled luxury. Sink into the supple leather seats and experience the seamless integration of advanced features, from the intuitive infotainment system to the responsive all-wheel-drive powertrain.

Beneath the sculpted hood, the 2.5L DOHC engine and CVT transmission deliver a thrilling yet efficient performance, with an impressive 42 MPG in the city and 41 MPG on the highway. The Crown Nightshade's dynamic handling and smooth ride quality will captivate you, whether navigating urban landscapes or embarking on open-road adventures.

Thoughtful details like the illuminated door sills, all-weather floor liners, and mudguards showcase the Crown Nightshade's commitment to both style and practicality. Indulge in the convenience of the power-adjustable, heated, and ventilated front seats, as well as the heated rear seats, ensuring comfort for all occupants.

Elevate your driving experience with the Crown Nightshade's comprehensive suite of advanced safety features, including the Blind Spot Monitor, Rear Cross-Traffic Alert, and Toyota Safety Sense 3.0. These cutting-edge technologies work seamlessly to help keep you and your loved ones secure on the road.

With a starting MSRP of $43,589, the 2026 Toyota Crown Nightshade represents exceptional value in the luxury sedan segment. Discover the perfect balance of style, performance, and technology that will elevate your driving experience. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate how the Crown Nightshade can exceed your expectations.

2023 BMW M440i Gran Coupe — 3L I-6 gasoline direct injection, DOHC, Double VANOS variable valve control, TwinPower intercooled turbo, premium unleaded, 382HP with 8-speed automatic — a sporty, four-door coupe that blends performance and everyday usability, with competitive fuel economy for its class, recent price adjustments make this an opportune time to buy before inventory changes.

Smart device integration makes it simple to mirror navigation, music and calls from your phone so you stay connected without taking your eyes off the road.

Forward collision mitigation constantly watches traffic ahead and can intervene to help prevent or lessen the impact of sudden stops, giving you greater peace of mind in busy driving conditions.

Pedestrian impact prevention enhances urban safety by detecting people on the roadway and taking proactive measures if a collision looks likely.

The rear camera provides a clear view behind the car to simplify parking and backing out, helping you avoid obstacles with more confidence.

Rear collision mitigation monitors the area behind the vehicle and prepares defensive responses if a rear impact becomes probable, helping protect occupants and reduce damage.

Brake assist senses emergency braking and applies maximum available stopping force to help you stop faster when every fraction of a second counts.

Selective internet access lets you personalize connected services so the vehicle delivers the news, updates and concierge features that matter most to you.

Cruise control with steering wheel-mounted controls maintains a preset speed and lets you adjust settings from the wheel to reduce fatigue on long drives while helping steady fuel use.

The power open and close liftgate offers hands-free convenience when loading cargo, making trips to the store or airport easier and faster.

Combining a potent inline-six engine and a refined 8-speed automatic with thoughtful safety, convenience and connectivity features, the 2023 BMW M440i Gran Coupe delivers engaging driving dynamics and real-world practicality—an appealing choice for buyers who want performance with everyday comfort, act soon to take advantage of current pricing and limited availability.

description: Discover the 2023 Porsche Taycan Base Sedan, an exceptional mix of electric performance and luxury. Finished in sleek black with a matching Basalt Black interior, this used Porsche combines sophisticated design with cutting-edge technology. With four doors and seating for four, it balances practicality and sporty elegance. Its RWD drivetrain delivers 402 horsepower and 254 lb-ft of torque, making every drive exhilarating. The Taycan’s remarkable efficiency is evident with an estimated 79 mpg in the city and 88 mpg on the highway, blending power with economy. Packed with innovative features, it includes Apple CarPlay, Bluetooth, a backup camera, and satellite radio readiness, ensuring seamless navigation and entertainment. Additional conveniences like heated seats, keyless entry, push start, a WiFi hotspot, wireless phone charging, lane keep assist, and collision warning elevate the driving experience, combining safety and luxury. This used Porsche Taycan also emphasizes safety and security through an advanced suite of features. Dual front knee airbags provide vital protection, complemented by traffic sign recognition that keeps you informed. Parking sensors at the front and rear assist with maneuvering in tight spots, while the regenerative braking system maximizes energy efficiency. The vehicle boasts 4-wheel ABS, an interior motion sensor anti-theft system, emergency braking preparation, and auto-locking power door locks for enhanced security. Painted brake calipers add a sporty aesthetic, completing the detail-oriented design that enhances both safety and style. 2023 Porsche Taycan Safety and Security Features Safety is a priority with dual front knee airbags offering critical protection. Traffic sign recognition helps keep you aware of road conditions, reducing accident risks. Parking sensors at front and rear aid in precise parking, while regenerative braking recovers energy during deceleration to extend range. The 4-wheel ABS improves braking performance, and the interior motion sensor anti-theft system helps prevent unauthorized access. Emergency braking preparation ensures quick response in critical moments, with power door locks featuring auto-locking for convenience. Painted brake calipers not only look sporty but support high-performance braking, adding to the vehicle’s safety credentials. 2023 Porsche Taycan Entertainment and Technology Features The infotainment system includes dual screens measuring 8.4 and 10.9 inches, providing clear visuals and intuitive controls. Porsche Connect compatibility allows for seamless smart device integration, while voice-operated hands-free calling and radio functions offer safer operation. The vehicle features ten premium speakers for immersive sound, along with HD radio and a touch screen display for easy media access. Real-time traffic data enhances navigation, and electronic messaging assistance with a read function keeps you connected without distraction. Auxiliary USB inputs provide additional connectivity options, making every drive engaging and connected. 2023 Porsche Taycan Performance Features This Taycan offers an impressive 200 miles per charge, supporting long-distance driving with confidence. Its active suspension, combined with electric suspension control and driver-adjustable ride control, delivers a smooth, customizable ride. The height adjustment feature enhances handling in different conditions. Powered by a lithium-ion battery, it supports DC fast charging, allowing a full recharge in just 9.5 hours on 240V outlets. These advanced performance features ensure the Taycan remains a leader among electric sport sedans, providing exhilarating driving dynamics without sacrificing practicality or efficiency.

description:
Mercedes-Benz of Palm Springs is delighted to showcase, this Certified Pre-Owned 2023 Mercedes-AMG C 43 Sedan. Finished in stunning Starling Blue Metallic and complemented by a Black Leather interior, with just 32,969 miles to its name, this performance-driven sedan delivers the perfect balance of everyday luxury and AMG-engineered excitement.

Bold, athletic, and unmistakably AMG, the C 43 Sedan makes a powerful first impression with its sculpted body lines, AMG body styling, and 19-inch AMG split 10-spoke wheels. Adaptive damping suspension, rear-axle steering, and advanced driver assistance technologies ensure precision handling and confidence in every driving scenario. This is a sedan engineered to thrill while maintaining Mercedes-Benz refinement.


Step inside and you are greeted by a driver-focused cockpit infused with premium materials and cutting-edge technology. Sport seats, the AMG Performance Steering Wheel in Nappa Leather, and illuminated AMG door sills reinforce its motorsport DNA. The MBUX multimedia system, augmented reality navigation, head-up display, and Burmester Surround Sound System elevate every journey with intuitive control and immersive sound.

Engine and Performance: At the heart of this AMG sedan is a handcrafted-inspired 2.0-liter turbocharged inline-4 engine with electric exhaust gas turbocharger and EQ Boost, producing a robust 402 horsepower and 369 lb-ft of torque. Paired with the lightning-quick 9G-TRONIC 9-speed automatic transmission and AMG Performance 4MATIC all-wheel drive, the C 43 delivers exhilarating acceleration, razor-sharp handling, and confident traction in all conditions.

Key Features:

• AMG Performance 4MATIC All-Wheel Drive: Delivers exceptional grip and dynamic handling for spirited driving.

• Rear-Axle Steering: Enhances agility at low speeds and stability at higher speeds for superior control.

• MBUX Multimedia System with Augmented Reality Navigation: Provides intuitive guidance and cutting-edge digital functionality.

• Burmester Surround Sound System: Premium audio clarity for an immersive listening experience.

• Head-Up Display: Keeps vital driving information directly in your line of sight.

• AMG Sport Seats & Ambient Lighting: Designed for both comfort and performance with a refined, modern atmosphere.

This 2023 Mercedes-AMG C 43 Sedan is more than just a luxury sedanit is a statement of performance, precision, and advanced engineering. Available now at Mercedes-Benz of Palm Springs, it offers an exceptional opportunity to experience AMG driving dynamics in a refined, everyday package.



Mercedes-Benz of Palm Springs is a member of the indiGO Auto Group. Our dealership features a beautiful showroom, fully staffed factory certified service center, parts department, finance department, detail department, and accessories boutique. Allow us to also help arrange transportation of your new car directly to your home anywhere in the world. Trade-in proposals are always welcome. If you like this vehicle and have questions, simply call, email, or drop by our location. We invite you to Activate Your Ownership with us today!

description:
Mercedes-Benz of Palm Springs is delighted to showcase, this Certified Pre-Owned 2023 Mercedes-Benz EQS 450 Sedan. Dressed in an elegant Obsidian Black Metallic exterior and complemented by a refined Neva Grey/Sable Brown Leather interior, with just 12,893 miles to its name, this all-electric luxury sedan represents the perfect balance of cutting-edge innovation, comfort, and Mercedes-Benz sophistication.

The EQS 450 Sedan sets a new benchmark for modern luxury, its sleek Obsidian Black Metallic exterior exuding presence and aerodynamic elegance. Equipped with the AMG Line Exterior Package, including AMG body styling and 21" AMG Multispoke Wheels with Black Accents, this EQS delivers a commanding stance. Advanced lighting technology such as DIGITAL LIGHT with projection functions, a Panorama Sunroof, and Surround View Camera further enhance both form and function.


Step inside and experience a sanctuary of refinement. The Neva Grey/Sable Brown Leather interior welcomes you with Multicontour Front Seats with Massage, Heated and Ventilated Front Seats, and a Four-Zone Climate Control System. Premium details such as Natural Grain Anthracite Linden Wood Trim, Active Ambient Lighting, and the immersive MBUX Hyperscreen with Navigation Premium elevate every drive into a first-class experience.

Engine and Performance: Powering this all-electric luxury sedan is a highly efficient electric motor producing 329 horsepower and an impressive 419 lb-ft of torque. Paired with a seamless single-speed automatic transmission and enhanced by AIRMATIC Air Suspension and Rear-Axle Steering, the EQS 450 delivers smooth, confident acceleration and exceptional ride comfort while maintaining remarkable efficiency.

Key Features:

• Driver Assistance Package: Includes Active Distance Assist DISTRONIC, Active Steering Assist, Active Lane Change Assist, and more for confident, semi-autonomous driving.

• Burmester Surround Sound System: A premium audio experience engineered to deliver concert-quality sound throughout the cabin.

• Head-Up Display: Projects critical driving information directly onto the windshield for enhanced focus and safety.

• MBUX Hyperscreen with Navigation Premium: A stunning digital interface combining driver display, central touchscreen, and passenger display into one seamless glass panel.

• ENERGIZING AIR CONTROL Plus with HEPA Filtration: Advanced cabin air filtration for superior comfort and air quality.

• KEYLESS-GO with HANDS-FREE ACCESS: Effortless entry and convenience designed around your lifestyle.

This Certified Pre-Owned 2023 Mercedes-Benz EQS 450 Sedan is far more than a vehicleit is a vision of the future, delivering sustainable performance without compromising luxury or innovation. Available now at Mercedes-Benz of Palm Springs, this EQS invites you to experience electric mobility at its finest.



Mercedes-Benz of Palm Springs is a member of the indiGO Auto Group. Our dealership features a beautiful showroom, fully staffed factory certified service center, parts department, finance department, detail department, and accessories boutique. Allow us to also help arrange transportation of your new car directly to your home anywhere in the world. Trade-in proposals are always welcome. If you like this vehicle and have questions, simply call, email, or drop by our location. We invite you to Activate Your Ownership with us today!

description:
Elevate your driving experience with this exceptional 2023 Lexus IS 350 F SPORT. This meticulously maintained, low-mileage vehicle offers a thrilling blend of performance, style, and advanced technology, making it the perfect choice for the discerning driver.

Boasting an impressive array of premium features, this IS 350 F SPORT is designed to exceed your expectations. Key highlights include:

• Intuitive Park Assist with Rear Cross-Traffic Braking
• Moonroof
• Accessory Package 2
• 10-Speaker Premium Audio System
• Apple CarPlay and Android Auto Integration

The 3.5L V6 DOHC Dual VVT-i engine, paired with an 8-speed automatic transmission, delivers an exhilarating driving experience with a perfect balance of power and efficiency. Enjoy an EPA-estimated 20 mpg in the city and 28 mpg on the highway, ensuring you can tackle your daily commute or weekend adventures with confidence.

This Lexus IS 350 F SPORT also comes with the added peace of mind of the Lexus L/Certified program. With Roadside Assistance, a $0 Warranty Deductible, and a comprehensive inspection, you can trust that this vehicle has been meticulously maintained and is ready to provide you with years of reliable performance.

The Lexus L/Certified warranty further enhances your ownership experience, offering the balance of the new car warranty (4 Year/50K Miles) plus an additional 2 Year/Unlimited-mileage L/Certified warranty. Additionally, you'll enjoy complimentary maintenance for the first four basic factory-scheduled services, ensuring your Lexus remains in top condition.

Elevate your driving experience and make this 2023 Lexus IS 350 F SPORT your own. Contact us today to schedule a test drive and discover the exceptional quality and performance that this vehicle has to offer.

Elevate your driving experience with this stunning 2025 Hyundai Elantra SEL Sport. This meticulously maintained sedan boasts a sleek red exterior that commands attention on the road. Powered by a fuel-efficient I4 engine and paired with a responsive CVT transmission, the Elantra delivers an impressive 30 city/39 highway MPG, making it the perfect companion for your daily commute or weekend adventures.

Highlighted features include:

• Blind Spot Monitor
• Push Button Start
• Ultimate Red exterior
• All-Season Fitted Liners
• Carpeted Floor Mats
• Front dual zone A/C
• Exterior Parking Camera Rear

The Elantra SEL Sport is equipped with a host of advanced safety and convenience features, ensuring a secure and comfortable driving experience. From the intuitive infotainment system with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto to the premium cloth seating, this vehicle is designed to cater to your every need.

As a Hyundai Certified Used Vehicle, this Elantra has undergone a rigorous 173+ point inspection, giving you the peace of mind that comes with a comprehensive warranty and roadside assistance coverage. With a Limited Warranty of 60 months/60,000 miles and a Powertrain Limited Warranty of 120 months/100,000 miles, you can drive with confidence, knowing your investment is protected.

We utilize Market Based Pricing for all pre-owned vehicles on our lot. This ensures you have the most competitive price in the market based on mileage, equipment, and features. Utilizing this approach, our prices may fluctuate during the day on our website and may not match what is currently on 3rd party sites as they only update every 24 hours. The Suntrup family have been servicing and selling cars since 1957 for the St Louis area.The Suntrup Automotive Group is active in its communities and believes in giving back. Today Suntrup Automotive Group has nine brands, eleven locations, thousands of cars and is every bit committed to providing excellent customer service in every aspect of the business. There's never been a better time to drop on by at our dealership here in 5926 So Lindbergh Blvd St Louis, Missouri, proudly serving drivers from Ballwin, Affton and Kirkwood. We're very much looking forward to it.

In developing our founding commitment ( The Cardinale Way ), we selected key words that are as meaningful to you as they are to our mission. One of those is “relationship.” With every introduction, we are looking, not for a single transaction, but to “develop” a relationship with our customers...not just a good relationship, but an “outstanding” relationship that will outlast your car. Another key element is that “everybody wins”. In a time when most people believe winners create losers, we endeavor to satisfy everybody involved. It means knowing our product well and our customer even better. It means listening and caring and understanding that people buy their second-most expensive item from people they trust. Whether you are a car enthusiast, or you just need a reliable ride, the right car for you means buying exactly what you need and ideally what you want. Over forty years ago, we entered the automobile business driven by a passion for people, and recognizing cars as a “vehicle” for creating meaningful connections. We also understood that helping people select, purchase and finance one of the most important tools of your daily life is a valuable pursuit. Our priority is and has always been making sure your new or used-car buying experience is both satisfying and successful. Within the Cardinale Automotive Group, we know that satisfying a wide range of needs requires a diversity of quality cars. We offer new Audi, BMW, GMC, Harley Davidson, Hyundai, Mazda, Nissan, Toyota and Volkswagen cars, along with used cars, trucks and SUVs by top manufacturers. We are committed to helping you find the right car, assisting you in choosing the right financing options, and becoming your trusted automobile dealer. Our relationship begins with our introduction and continues through the purchase, the financing, the service of the car and beyond. We look forward to developing an outstanding relationship with you.

Quick Order Package 22R
    Comfort
    • Ventilated front seats -That's cool. Ventilated front seats provides targeted cool air so you and your passenger can get comfortable quicker in hot weather. Getting comfortable is no sweat when you have ventilated front seats.
    Convenience
    • Smart device and keyfob engine start control - Phone ahead. Remotely start your vehicle's engine from the key fob or your smart device, ensuring your ride is ready to go when you get in. Now you can stay comfortable inside while your vehicle gets comfortable outside, ,thanks to Smart device and Keyfob engine start control.
    • Power open and close liftgate - On-demand access. When your arms are full of cargo, the last thing you want to do is set it all down just to open the liftgate, then pick it all back up to load it in. By remotely opening and closing, power liftgate lets you skip straight to the loading. It also eliminates the awkward stretch to reach up for the liftgate to close it. Load and go with power open and close liftgate.
    Technology and Telematics
    • Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road.
    • Voice activated integrated navigation system - A to B made easy! Whether it's an errand or a road trip, the voice activated integrated navigation system will guide you to your destination. No more bulky, impossible-to-fold maps, and no more stopping to ask for directions. Just tell it where you want to go, and the voice activated integrated navigation system shows you the right way.

Choose Habberstad BMW of Huntington and experience first-hand our unwavering commitment to exceptional customer service, care, and satisfaction. Welcome to a new standard of automotive excellence.

At McGrath Lexus of Westmont, we want to help you find your dream car. We are dedicated to serving our guests by delivering impeccable customer service and a commitment to excellence. We are proud recipients of the Lexus' League of Elite Award. The Elite Award represents the highest level of customer satisfaction and we are one of the three stores to achieve this in the entire nation.

The customer relationship begins the moment we greet you, and throughout the duration of your Lexus vehicle ownership which continues with award-winning service and support that is sure to exceed your expectations.

Certified. Certification Program Details: Why L/Certified by Lexus? 2023 marks the sixth year in a row that U.S. News & World Report has named L/Certified by Lexus the “Best CPO Program”. With industry-leading benefits, innovative design and thrilling performance, L/Certified by Lexus puts your dream car in your driveway.

161-POINT INSPECTION: Each L/Certified by Lexus vehicle undergoes a comprehensive 161-point inspection.

WARRANTY: Lexus confidently stands behind these exceptional vehicles with the L/Certified Limited Warranty,* which when combined with the new-vehicle Basic Warranty, can provide up to six years of vehicle warranty coverage. Mileage is unlimited. The L/Certified Limited Warranty offers many of the coverage benefits and privileges new-car buyers receive.

The L/Certified Limited Warranty* includes coverage for a complimentary loaner car,* Roadside Assistance* and Trip Interruption Service.* There is no deductible.

COMPLIMENTARY MAINTENANCE: From the day you purchase your L/Certified Vehicle, you receive Complimentary Maintenance covering the next four factory-recommended services for two years or 20,000 miles, whichever comes first.*

ROADSIDE ASSISTANCE: Every L/Certified vehicle comes with the reassurance of Lexus Roadside Assistance.

TRIP PROTECTION: If your vehicle has mechanical difficulty while you're away from home, you will be reimbursed for meals and lodging for a maximum of three nights (up to $200 per night) while repairs are performed on your car, in addition to reimbursement for a rental car for up to five days (up to $50 per day)*.

LOANER CAR: a loaner vehicle can be provided free of charge.


**All McGrath Lexus customer’s get complimentary car washes.**

Find out why everyone loves McGrath Lexus of Westmont and is one of three Lexus dealerships in the nation to achieve the Lexus' League of Elite Award!

Safety and Security
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
  • Hands-on cruise control. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful. Cruise control only managed speed, but not distance or safety. Now, with hands-on cruise control, simply set your desired speed and let sensor technology maintain a safe distance between you and surrounding vehicles. It slows you down, speeds you up and even keeps you in your own lane. Meet your ultimate co-pilot with hands-on cruise control.
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
Technology and Telematics
  • Audi smartphone interface w/wireless Apple CarPlay smart device wireless mirroring
  • Mobile hotspot - WiFi on the fly. Connect your devices to the Internet through your vehicle's private mobile hotspot and take the internet wherever your journey takes you, without eating up your data allowance. Find the hotspot with mobile hotspot.

Safety and Security
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
  • Hands-on cruise control. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful. Cruise control only managed speed, but not distance or safety. Now, with hands-on cruise control, simply set your desired speed and let sensor technology maintain a safe distance between you and surrounding vehicles. It slows you down, speeds you up and even keeps you in your own lane. Meet your ultimate co-pilot with hands-on cruise control.
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
Technology and Telematics
  • Audi smartphone interface w/wireless Apple CarPlay smart device wireless mirroring
  • Mobile hotspot - WiFi on the fly. Connect your devices to the Internet through your vehicle's private mobile hotspot and take the internet wherever your journey takes you, without eating up your data allowance. Find the hotspot with mobile hotspot.

This 2025 Audi A5 Premium Plus, has a exterior and a interior color. 4,189 miles. Stock Number SL4451. You can connect with us by calling (704) 535-8800. No Accidents! One Owner! Important Package and Feature Information Premium Plus ($3,600 value)
  • Panoramic Glass with Variable Light Control
  • Bang & Olufsen Sound System with 3D Sound
  • Animation For Taillights
  • Adaptive Cruise Assist
  • Dynamic Interaction Light
  • Head-Up Display
  • LED Interior Lighting Pro Package
  • LED Headlights Plus with Digital DRL
  • Park Assist Plus
  • Heated Steering Wheel with Hands-On Detection
  • Top View Camera System
  • USB Power Delivery (2x60W Front and 2x100W Rear)
Safety and Security
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
  • Hands-on cruise control. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful. Cruise control only managed speed, but not distance or safety. Now, with hands-on cruise control, simply set your desired speed and let sensor technology maintain a safe distance between you and surrounding vehicles. It slows you down, speeds you up and even keeps you in your own lane. Meet your ultimate co-pilot with hands-on cruise control.
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
Technology and Telematics
  • Audi smartphone interface w/wireless Apple CarPlay smart device wireless mirroring
  • Mobile hotspot - WiFi on the fly. Connect your devices to the Internet through your vehicle's private mobile hotspot and take the internet wherever your journey takes you, without eating up your data allowance. Find the hotspot with mobile hotspot.

description:
This Factory Certified 2025 Genesis G70 3.3T Sport Prestige, has a Uyuni White exterior and an Fog Gray Two-Tone interior color. 6,254 miles. Stock Number SU147208. You can connect with us by calling (407) 628-4343. Wheels: 19\' x 8.0J Fr & 19\' x 8.5J Rr Sport Alloy, Express Open/Close Sliding And Tilting Glass 1st Row Sunroof w/Power Sunshade, Perimeter/Approach Lights, 15 Speakers, 2 LCD Monitors In The Front, Real-Time Traffic Display, Perimeter Alarm, Highway Driving Assist (HDA)/Lane Follow Assist (LFA), Blind-spot Collision-Avoidance Assist (BCA) Blind Spot, Forward Collision-Avoidance Assist (fca), Rear Cross-Traffic Collision Avoidance-Assist (RCCA), Collision Mitigation-Front, Driver Monitoring-Alert, Front And Rear Parking Sensors No Accidents! One Owner! OTHER NOTABLE FEATURES AND OPTIONS YOU SHOULD KNOW ABOUT: Sport Prestige Package ($4,400 value)
    Option Group 04
    • Electronically Controlled Suspension
    • Heated Steering Wheel
    • Microfiber Suede Headliner and Pillars
    • Head-Up Display (HUD)
    • Limited-Slip Differential
    • Nappa Leather Seating Surfaces
    • Surround View Monitor with Blind Spot View Monitor
    • Power Trunk
    Convenience
    • GPS linked cruise control - Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful, until GPS linked cruise control set the pace. Simply set the desired speed and the system uses GPS navigation data to maintain that speed without driver intervention - including slowing down for curves and anticipating hills. This can help minimize driver fatigue and improve overall fuel economy. Meet your ultimate co-pilot, GPS linked cruise control.
    Safety and Security
    • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
    • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
    • Hands-on cruise control. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful. Cruise control only managed speed, but not distance or safety. Now, with hands-on cruise control, simply set your desired speed and let sensor technology maintain a safe distance between you and surrounding vehicles. It slows you down, speeds you up and even keeps you in your own lane. Meet your ultimate co-pilot with hands-on cruise control.
    Technology and Telematics
    • Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road.
    SPORT PRESTIGE PACKAGE, FOG GRAY TWO-TONE, NAPPA LEATHER SEATING SURFACES, ILLUMINATED DOOR SCUFF PLATES All of our vehicles are clearly marked with our haggle-free best price and our sales associates are commission-free. That means they'll help you find the car that fits you best, not the one that earns them the biggest commission check. Every vehicle we sell comes with guaranteed peace of mind. Unhappy with your purchase? Take advantage of our market-leading return policy and bring it back within five days or three hundred miles, plain and simple. Just Add Tax, Tag, Title/Registration and other government required charges. Vehicles which are registered outside the state of Florida will incur a $495.00 fee to cover additional costs of titling, registration, administrative resources and document shipping. This fee also represents costs and profit to the dealer for items such as inspecting, cleaning and adjusting vehicles, and preparing documents related to the sale. No surprises, no hassles! While every reasonable effort is made to ensure the accuracy of this information, we are not responsible for any errors or omissions contained on these pages. Please verify any information in question with us.

2025 BMW 330i xDrive Sedan
Step into the world of luxury and performance with the 2025 BMW 330i xDrive Sedan. This exquisite vehicle seamlessly combines cutting-edge technology with a spirited driving experience, making every journey an adventure. Dressed in the stunning Skyscraper Grey Metallic, the sleek exterior is complemented by the inviting Canberra Beige Perforated Sensatec interior, creating an ambiance that speaks to sophistication and comfort. With its xDrive all-wheel drive system, the 330i offers exceptional handling and stability, ensuring that you can tackle any road or weather condition with confidence.

Inside, you’ll find a suite of features designed to enhance your driving pleasure. The Convenience Package includes power front seats with lumbar support and heated front seats, ensuring that every ride is as comfortable as it is exhilarating. Stay connected with the Harman Kardon surround sound system and enjoy the modern conveniences of Wireless Device Charging and Apple CarPlay/Android Auto Compatibility. With the Active Driving Assistant, you’ll have peace of mind knowing that advanced safety features are working to protect you and your passengers. The 330i xDrive Sedan is not just a car, it's a lifestyle choice that embodies the essence of BMW's commitment to performance and luxury.

Embrace the unparalleled luxury and performance of the 2025 BMW 330i xDrive Sedan—where every detail is crafted for your driving pleasure.

description:
2025 Mercedes-Benz C 300 4MATIC Sedan Low-Mileage, Feature-Rich, and Elegantly Appointed
Offered in classic Polar White over refined Sienna Brown MB-Tex, this 2025 C 300 4MATIC combines all-weather confidence with executive-level comfort and modern Mercedes-Benz technology. With just 5,972 miles, this sedan presents an exceptional opportunity to own a nearly-new luxury vehicle at outstanding value.

Originally priced at $52,885 MSRP, this C-Class is outfitted with several desirable options and packages that elevate your daily drive:
Highlighted Features & Packages:
- Panorama Sunroof expansive glass roof enhances cabin openness and elegance ($1,000)
- Heated Steering Wheel added cold-weather comfort ($250)
- Advanced Package (PDA) includes MBUX Navigation with Augmented Video, enhanced driver display, and more
- Winter Package (PAV) tailored for Northeast driving with heated convenience and functionality
- 18" 5-Spoke Alloy Wheels on All-Season Tires (R02) with Extended Mobility capability
- Fineline Anthracite Wood Trim (H08) a tasteful complement to the Sienna Brown interior
- HANDS-FREE ACCESS (871) open the trunk with a kick of your foot
- Apple CarPlay & Android Auto seamless smartphone integration
- Power Folding Mirrors and Auto-Dimming Rearview/Driver Mirrors
Service & Ownership History:
Originally placed in service in February 2025, this C 300 has had two owners beginning as a corporate fleet vehicle before being titled for personal use. The vehicle has remained in Ohio since new, and was serviced by Mercedes-Benz of North Olmsted throughout, including a four-wheel alignment and detailing in June 2025. The mileage is significantly lower than average for its age, further enhancing its appeal and long-term value.
Warranty Coverage:
Still under the balance of the 4-year/50,000-mile New Vehicle Limited Warranty, with an estimated 38 months or 44,005 miles of factory coverage remaining. Please confirm warranty expiration with dealership for accuracy.

Luxury Value, Transparent Pricing, and a Dealer You Can Trust
At Mercedes-Benz of North Olmsted, we're transforming the dealership experience. Our Worry-Free Pricing ensures a hassle-free process no pressure, no games just transparent, market-based pricing from the start, giving you complete confidence while you shop.

We proudly serve local and out-of-town clients nationwide, offering luxury expertise, white-glove service, and seamless remote sales support. Whether you're shopping from across the street or across the country, our reputation for competitive pricing and exceptional vehicles makes us your destination for Mercedes-Benz.

This stunning 2025 Lexus IS 350 F SPORT is a true standout in the luxury sedan segment. With its sleek and aggressive styling, powerful performance, and impressive list of premium features, this vehicle is sure to capture the attention of discerning drivers.

• One Owner
• Front dual zone A/C
• Moonroof
• Electronic Stability Control
• Auto High-beam Headlights
• Fully automatic headlights
• Apple CarPlay/Android Auto
• Garage door transmitter: HomeLink
• Heated front seats
• Wheels: 19" Split-5-Spoke Alloy with Dark Metallic Finish
• Rain sensing wipers

The heart of this IS 350 F SPORT is a potent 3.5L V6 DOHC Dual VVT-i 24V engine, paired with an 8-Speed Automatic transmission and rear-wheel drive. This powertrain delivers an exhilarating driving experience, with 311 horsepower and 280 lb-ft of torque on tap. Yet, it still manages an impressive 20 MPG in the city and 28 MPG on the highway, making it a practical choice for daily commutes and weekend getaways alike.

Lexus is renowned for its commitment to quality, and this L/Certified IS 350 F SPORT is no exception. With a comprehensive inspection, an unlimited-mileage warranty for up to 6 years, and complimentary maintenance for the first 2 years or 20,000 miles, you can have peace of mind knowing that your investment is well-protected.

The interior of this Lexus is equally impressive, with a host of premium features that elevate the driving experience. Highlights include dual-zone automatic climate control, a power-adjustable driver's seat with memory settings, a heated steering wheel, and a premium audio system with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto integration. The sporty F SPORT-tuned suspension and steering provide a dynamic and engaging driving feel, while the advanced safety technologies, such as electronic stability control and a rearview camera, help keep you and your passengers secure.

With its exceptional performance, luxurious amenities, and the added benefits of Lexus' renowned certification program, this 2025 IS 350 F SPORT is a remarkable opportunity for the discerning driver. We invite you to experience this exceptional vehicle for yourself by scheduling a test drive at our showroom. We're confident that once you get behind the wheel, you'll be captivated by its unparalleled blend of style, power, and sophistication.

Discover the exceptional 2025 Genesis G70 3.3T Sport Advanced, a true testament to the brand's commitment to performance and luxury. This meticulously maintained vehicle, with only 2,248 miles, offers a captivating blend of style, power, and advanced features that will elevate your driving experience.

• Clean Vehicle History * No Accidents
• Remainder of Factory Warranty Package Available
• Uyuni White

• Mudguards

Beneath the sleek, white exterior lies the heart of a true driving enthusiast's dream – a potent 3.3L V6 DGI DOHC 24V engine paired with an 8-Speed Automatic transmission and Rear-Wheel Drive. This powertrain delivers an exhilarating 17 city/25 highway MPG, ensuring you can explore the open road with confidence and efficiency.

The Genesis G70 3.3T Sport Advanced is more than just a performance-oriented sedan, it's a masterpiece of design and technology. Indulge in the luxurious leather seating, which can be both heated and ventilated for year-round comfort. The 15-speaker Lexicon Premium Audio System will immerse you in a concert-hall-like experience, while the intuitive touchscreen display with Android Auto and Apple CarPlay integration keeps you connected and in control.

Safety is paramount, and the G70 3.3T Sport Advanced delivers with a comprehensive suite of advanced driver-assistance features. From the Blind Spot Monitoring System to the Rear Cross-Traffic Alert, you can navigate with confidence, knowing that your vehicle is looking out for you.

As you settle into the driver's seat, you'll be greeted by a thoughtfully designed cabin that seamlessly blends form and function. The power-adjustable seats with memory settings ensure a personalized driving position, while the heated steering wheel and dual-zone automatic climate control provide an exceptional level of comfort.

This 2025 Genesis G70 3.3T Sport Advanced is more than just a car – it's an opportunity to elevate your driving experience. With its impressive performance, luxurious amenities, and advanced safety features, this vehicle is poised to exceed your expectations. We invite you to schedule a test drive and discover the true essence of the Genesis brand for yourself.

description:
Elevate your driving experience with this exceptional 2025 Mercedes-Benz C-Class C 43 AMG® 4MATIC®. This sophisticated and dynamic sedan is poised to captivate with its exceptional performance, cutting-edge technology, and unparalleled craftsmanship.

Discover a curated selection of premium features that elevate this C-Class to new heights:

• Burmester® 3D Surround Sound System
• Adaptive suspension
• Power moonroof
• Augmented Video for Navigation
• Head-Up Display with AMG® Specific Content
• Power Heated Front Seats with Memory
• Heated front seats

Immerse yourself in the pinnacle of automotive luxury with the Individualization Package and Pinnacle Trim Package, which offer a wealth of enhancements to elevate your driving experience.

Beneath the sleek exterior lies a powerful I4 engine mated to a 9-Speed Automatic transmission with 4MATIC® all-wheel drive. This dynamic powertrain delivers an exhilarating 19 city/27 highway MPG, ensuring both performance and efficiency.

The striking White exterior exudes a timeless elegance, while the meticulously crafted interior with MB-Tex/Microfiber upholstery provides a serene and sophisticated ambiance. Cutting-edge technologies, including the 11.9" Center Touchscreen Display, Apple CarPlay®/Android Auto®, and the DIGITAL LIGHT with Projections, seamlessly integrate to elevate your driving experience.

Safety is paramount, and this C-Class is equipped with a comprehensive suite of advanced driver assistance features, including Adaptive Cruise Control, Blind Spot Monitoring, and Lane Keeping Assist, ensuring your peace of mind on every journey.

This exceptional 2025 Mercedes-Benz C-Class C 43 AMG® 4MATIC® is a true testament to the brand's dedication to excellence. Experience the pinnacle of luxury, performance, and technology by scheduling a test drive at our showroom today. We look forward to the opportunity to demonstrate how this remarkable vehicle can transform your driving experience.
